quran[668]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,Yettoore nden ko Allah jooma tageefu On woodani
  1,2,Jooma yurmeende hu…ďtidinnde e heeriinde
  1,3,Jooma √Īalngu njo…ďdiiji
  1,4,Ko Aan tan min ndewata te ko Aan tan min mballintoo
  1,5,Feewnu min e laawol pooccingol
  1,6,Laawol ngol …ďeen …ďe neemin-…óaa …ďe ngonaa tikkanaa…ďe te …ďe majjaani
  2,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  2,2,"Ndeen deftere sikke alaa he mayre, ko nde peewal wonande hul…ďe …ďe"
  2,3,∆Āeen goon…óinoo…ďe mbirniindi e…ďe √Īii…ďna juulde e…ďe nafga e ko Min nje…ói …ďe
  2,4,"E …ďeen goon…óinoo…ďe ko Min njippini dow maa e ko jippinaa ado ma, e…ďe njananaa √Īalaande wattan"
  2,5,"∆Āeen dey ngoni ko e peewal iwngal e Joomii …ďe, ko kam…ďe ngoni da…óoo…ďe"
  2,6,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe ngoon…óintaa foti a jeertinii …ďe wolla a jeertinaani, fof foti e mum en"
  2,7,"Alla muppi …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, wirngallo woni noppi e gite ma…ď…ďe lette maw…óe na woodani …ďe"
  2,8,"Na woodi heen yim…ďe wi'oo…ďe min ngoon…óinii Alla e √Īalaande wattan, tawa …ďe ngoon…óinaani"
  2,9,"E…ďe koda Alla e goon…óin…ďe …ďe, alaa mbo …ďe kodata sonaa ko'e ma…ď…ďe tawa …ďe nganndaa"
  2,10,Ko √Īawo woni e …ďer…óe Alla …ďeydani …ďe √Īawu maa lette muus…óe njan e mum en sabu ko …ďe pennannoo
  2,11,So …ďe mbi'aama taa bonnee e lesdi ndi …ďe mbi'a minen ko min mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe
  2,12,Ko kam…ďe tigi ngoni bonnoo…ďe kono …ďe tinataa …óum
  2,13,"So …ďe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee wano yim…ďe …ďee ngoon…óiri, …ďe mbi'a mbela minen ngoon…óina wano …óaay…ďe …ďee ngoon…óiniri, kono ko kam…ďe tigi ngoni …óaay…ďe kono …ďe nganndaa"
  2,14,"So tawii …ďe kawrii e goon…óin…ďe …ďe mbi'a: min ngoon…óinii, so …ďe njeewdii e sey…óanooji ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe mbi'a: minen ko onon min ngonndi min njalkitat tan"
  2,15,Alla jalkita …ďe O …ďeydana …ďe bewre …ďe ngona e wemmbere
  2,16,"Ko …ďeen ngoni soodir…ďe peewal majjere njeeygu ma…ď…ďe alaa tono, te …ďe peewaano"
  2,17,∆Āe nanndi ko e ku…ď…ďu…óo jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre ma…ď…ďe O acci …ďe e ni…ďe …ďe nji'ataa hay huunde
  2,18,Ko fah…óu…ďe muum…óu…ďe wum…ďe …ďe nduttotaako
  2,19,Wolla wano to…ďo iwde asamaan na woodi ni…ďe e digaali e maje …ďe cukka noppi ma…ď…ďe sabu kartaali (par√Īite) ngam reentaade maayde Alla noon Ombo hi…ďindii ge…óe heefer…ďe
  2,20,"Majal ngal na …óe…ďa yulde gite ma…ď…ďe kala nde ngal yaynii …ďe njaha heen so ni…ď…ďi…óii …ďe ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nan…óe e gite ma…ď…ďe sabu Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,21,Onon yim…ďe ndewee Jooma mon tag…óo on tagi adii…ďe on mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,22,"Oon mba…óan…óo on lesdi ndi mbertu O wa…ói Asamaan o mahoodi tii…óndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe woni nje…óu mon, taa mba…óanee Alla nanndidii…ďe te o…óon nganndi goonga o"
  2,23,"So tawii o…óon cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaa…óo Amen o, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, nodde wallidii…ďe mon gaa Alla so tawii o…óon ngoon…ói e nodditaandu mon ndu"
  2,24,"So tawii on mba…óaani …óum -te on mbaawataa …óum- kulee jayngol ku…ď…ďirtengol yim…ďe e kaa∆īe, ngol heblanaa ko heefer…ďe …ďe"
  2,25,"Weltin …ďeen goon…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi wonde …ďe…ď ke…ďa aljannaaji caalli na ndonga les majji kala nde …ďe nje…óaa toon …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe …ďe mbi'a ko …óee min nje…óanoo ko adii, kono si …ďe mee…óii …óe …ďe tawa e…óe ceerti, e…ďe ke…ďa toon rew…ďe laa…ď…ďe …ďe √Īii…ďida toon. @Corrected"
  2,26,"Alla aamantaa addude yeru hay so wonii wano …ďowngu e ko …ďuri …óum, so tawii ko goon…óin…ďe e…ďe nganndi ko goonga iw…óo e Jooma ma…ď…ďe, so tawii ko yeddu…ďe …ďe mbi'a holko Alla yi…ói e oo yeru Ombo majjina heew…ďe O feewna heen heew…ďe, alaa majjintee…óo heen sonaa yaltu…ďe …óoftaare. @Corrected"
  2,27,∆Āeen firtoo…ďe aadi Alla …ďaawo tii…óneede mbo e…ďe ta∆īa ko Alla yamiri yo jokke e…ďe mbonna ka lesdi ko kam…ďe ngoni rus…ďii…ďe (pertu…ďe)
  2,28,Holno njeddirton Alla tawa ngoodaano O wuurni on rewa heen O wara on rewa heen O wuurtina on …ďaawo …óuum ko e Makko nduttoto-…óon
  2,29,Kanko tagani on kala ko woni e lesdi ndi …ďaawo …óuum O faandii asamaan O fotndi mbo asamaanji jee…ói…ói Kanko ganndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected
  2,30,"Nde Joom maa wi'i malayka en maa Mi wa…ó lomto Am e lesdi ndi, …ďe mbi'i mbela wa…óat heen bonnoowo dufoowo ∆īii∆īe tawa minen ko Aan tan min njettata mi…óen Ma teddina, O wi'i Miin Mi…óo anndi ko on nganndaa"
  2,31,"O anndini Aadama in…óe …óe fofo, rewi heen O holli …óe malaykaa…ďe …ďe O wi'i kaalanee Kam in…óe …ďee …óoo so tawii o…óon ngoon…ói"
  2,32,∆Āe mbi'i senaande woodanii Ma alaa ko min nganndi sonaa ko nganndin-∆äaa min ko Aan tan woni ganndid…óo kala huunde √Īee√Ī…óu…óo
  2,33,O wi'i aan Aadama anndin …ďe in…óe majji nde o anndini …ďe in…óe …óee O wi'i mbela Mi wi'aano on Miin Mi…óo anndi mbirniindi asamanji e lesdi Mi…óo anndi ko pe√Ī√Īinton e ko cuu…óoton fof
  2,34,Nde Min mbii malaykaa…ďe …ďe cujjanee Aadama …ďe cujji sonaa Ibliisa o salii o mawnikinii ndeen o jeyaa e yeddu…ďe
  2,35,Min mbii aan Aadama yah ho…óoy aljanna aan e debbo maa √Īaamee toon ko welata on kala …óo mbela-…óon taa …ďado-…óee kii lekki ndeen on jeyete e too√Ī…ďe
  2,36,Sey…óaane hoomti …ďe haa yaltini …ďe e mo∆ī∆īere nde …ďe ngonndoo Min mbii …ďe njippo-…óee ngonon a√Īondir…ďe ke…ďon √Īii…ďal dow lesdi ndi e dakmitaare haa happu yonta
  2,37,Aadama he…ďi konngi iwde e Joom mum O accani mo ko Kanko woni jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo
  2,38,Min mbi'i njippo-…óee toon onon fof so tawii Mi addii e mon peewal kala dew…óo peewam Am …ďeen dey kulol alanaa …ďe kadi …ďe cunotaako
  2,39,∆Āeen yeddu…ďe penni maandeeji Amen ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe jayngol ko toon …ďe √Īii…ďata
  2,40,Onon …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil ciftoree mo∆ī∆īere Am nde Mi wa…óani on njottinee aadi Am Mi yottina aadi mon te kulon Kam Miin tan
  2,41,"Ngoon…óinee ko njippin-Mi na goon…óini ko njogi-…óon ko taa ngonee adii…ďe yeddude …óum wota on eto soodirde aayeeje am …óe coggu hoyngu, kulee kam Miin tan"
  2,42,Taa jii…ďindiree goonga e fenaande o…óon cuu…óa goonga o tawa o…óon nganndi mbo
  2,43,√Ďii…ďnee juulde tottiron asakal …óigganon njankinano-…óon Alla
  2,44,"Mbela on njamirat yim…ďe …óiggere njejjiton ko'e mon tawa o…óon njanga deftere nde, mbela on kakkilantaa …óum"
  2,45,"Mballitoree mu√Īal e juulde, pellet honde sa…ótani dow mbo yankinii…ďe …ďe"
  2,46,∆Āeen yananaa…ďe maa kawru e joom ma…ď…ďe ko he Makko …ďe nduttotoo
  2,47,"Onon …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil ciftoree neemaaji Am …ói neemin MI mon, ko Miin tigi …ďurni e dow winndre he"
  2,48,Kulee √Īande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu ndu ja…ďantaake tefangol go…ó…óo coodtiigu kadi ja…ďetaake …ďe ke…ďataa ballo
  2,49,"Tuma Min ndanndii on yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďe mba…óii on lette bon…óe …ďe kirsa …ďi…ď…ďe mon …ďe ngoppa rew…ďe mon nguura, ina e …óuum lette maw…óe iwde ga Jooma mon"
  2,50,Nde Min peccani on maayo ngo Min ndanndi on Min njooli yim…ďe Fir'awna o…óon ndaarda gite mon Ňčaas
  2,51,Nde Min podani Muusaa jammaaji capan…óe nayi fawii heen ndew-…óon ngaari ndi caggal Am onon ko on too√Īoo…ďe
  2,52,Fawii heen Min ngaccani on …ďaawo …óuum mbela joo njetton
  2,53,Nde Min ngaddani Muusa deftere nde e Furgaana mbela joo peewon
  2,54,Nde Muusaa wi'i yim…ďe makko onon yim…ďe am on too√Īii ko'e mon nde ndew-…óon ngaari ndi ndutto…óee e tag…óo on o mbarto-…óon …óuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īande on to Jooma mon O accana on Kanko woni gaccanoowo njurmotoo…óo
  2,55,Nde mbii-…óon Muusaa min ngoon…óitaa haa min nji'a Alla ko laa…ďi ndeen hartaango (jayngol iwde asamaan) …ďami on o…óon ndaarda gite mon
  2,56,Fawii heen Min nguurtini on …ďaawo nde maay-…óon mbela joo njetton
  2,57,"Min …óuwdini on duule Min njippinani on njuumri dakmundi e colli ju…óaa…ói √Īaamee e bel…ói ko Min nje…ói on, wonaa Minen …ďe too√Īi ko ko'e ma…ď…ďe …ďe too√Īatnoo"
  2,58,Min mbii naatee ndee saare √Īaamon heen ko mbela-…óon mbeltoron naatee damal ngal o…óon njankinii mbi'on accan min ndeen Min njaafoo on goopi mon Min …ďeydana mo∆ī∆īin…ďe …ďee mo∆ī∆īereeji
  2,59,Too√Ī…ďe …ďee mbayliti konngol ngol …ďe mbi'anoo ndeen Min njippini dow too√Īoo…ďe …ďee lette sabu ko …ďe ngonno ko faasqeebe
  2,60,"Nde Muusaa toranii yim…ďe mum ndiyam Min mbi'i fiyu haayre nde sawru maa ndu ndeen gite ndiyam sappo e …ói…ói puccitii heen yim…ďe …ďee fof ke…ďi yarde, √Īaamee njaree e nje…óu Alla taa mba…óee bonannde dow lesdi ndi"
  2,61,"Nde mbii-…óon aan Muusaa min min njondintaako e √Īaamdu wooturu torano min Joom maa O yaltinana min pu…ói lesdi gila e kappe e haakooji e buudi e √Īebbe e basalle (jabaa) mayri o, wi'i mbela on nji…ó lomtinde ko ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko, ke…ďon ko …ďuri jaasde …óuum njippo-…óee Misara maa on ke…ď ko tori-…óon ko …ďe pawaa koyeera e woro…óde …ďe nduttorii e tikkere Alla sabu …ďe njedduno aayeeje e…ďe mbara Annabaa…ďe ko aldaa e goonga …óuum noon ko goopi e too√Īe ma…ď…ďe"
  2,62,"∆Āeen goon…óin…ďe e…ď…ďen feew…ďe e nasaara en e …ďe ngalaa diine,kala goon…óin…óo Alla e √Īalaande wattan o golli ko mo∆ī∆īi …ďeen ke…ďata njo…ďdi to Jooma ma…ď…ďe kulol alanaa …ďe te kam…ďe …ďe cunotaako"
  2,63,Nde Min …ďami aadi mon Min ummini fello Tuur dow mon ∆īettee ko Min ngddani on e semmbe ciftoree ko woni heen mbela joo kulon Alla
  2,64,Fawii heen caggal …óuum nduŇčti-…óon taw naano …ďural Alla e yurmeende Makko dow mon maa on njeye e bonnoraa…ďe
  2,65,On nganndii …ďeen too√Ī…ďe e mon √Īande hoore-biir (samdi) Min mbii …ďe ngontee baa…ói booraa…ói
  2,66,Min mba…ói …óum woni maande teskuye wonande …ďe e aroyoo…ďe e tinndinoore wonande hul…ďe Alla …ďe
  2,67,"Muusaa wi'i yim…ďe makko Alla yamirii on nde kirsoton nagge …ďe mbii mbela nanngir-…óaa min ko …óaay…ďe? o wi'i: mi…óo moolii Alla jeyeede e majju…ďe"
  2,68,"∆Āe mbii du'ano min Jooma maa O la…ď…ďinana min no nge wa'i. O wii: ko nge wonaa nayeye wonaa √Īalel ko hakindiinge mba…óee ko njamira-…óon ko"
  2,69,"∆Āe mbii torano min Jooma maa O la…ď…ďinana min ngoobu (kulor) magge ? O wii: Oon wii ko sooye no feewi enge weli laarde"
  2,70,∆Āe mbii du'ano min Joom maa O la…ď…ďinana min no nge wa'i sabu na'i …ói nanndiri min maa min njiitu nge
  2,71,"O wi'i Kanko dee O wii ko nagge ne'iraange golle remru ngesa, kono wonaa yarnude gese, ko hisnge nge jillaani, …ďe mbii jooni dey a addii goonga …ďe kirsi nge kono …ďe …óe…ďaani wa…óde yamiroore nde"
  2,72,Nde mbar-…óon fettaandu ngon-…óon e tuumondirde ko Alla yaltini ko cuu…óno-…óon
  2,73,Min mbii tappindiree …ói ko noon Alla wuurtinirta maay…ďe O holla on kaawase Makko mbela joo kakkilon
  2,74,"Fawii heen …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óe njoori …ďaawo …óuum …óe mba'i no kaa∆īe maa …ďura noon, sabu kaa∆īe na ngoodi jaltinooje caalli go…ó…óe na peecoo njaltina ndiyam go…ó…óe kadi njowtoo janansabu hulde Alla, Alla noo yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,75,Mbela o…óon …óaminii maa …ďe ngoon…óinan on tawa na woodi e ma…ď…ďe sete nanoowo haala Alla …ďe mbaylita ka caggal nde …ďe paami …ďe nganndi ka
  2,76,"So …ďe kawri e goon…óin…ďe …ďee …ďe mbii min ngoon…óinii so …ďe njeewdii …ďe mbi'a mbela on kaalanat …ďe ko Alla udditani on, ndeen …ďe ka…ďora on …óum to Jooma mon, mbela on kakkilantaa"
  2,77,Mbela …ďe nganndataa wonde Alla Mbo anndi ko …ďe cuu…óta e ko …ďe …ďaŇčnginta
  2,78,"Na woodi e mum en humambinnee…ďe …ďe nganndaa e deftere nde sonaa janngugol penaale …óe …ďe nganndinaa, …ďe ngoni e sikkude tan"
  2,79,"Bone woodanii …ďeen winndiroo…ďe deftere nde juu…óe ma…ď…ďe e…ďe mbi'a …óum ko to Alla iwri haa …ďe coodira nde coggu hoyngu, bone wonan …ďe e ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe mbinndi e kala ko …ďe paggitii heen"
  2,80,∆Āe mbii jayngol memataa min sinaa bal…óe see…óa wii …ďe mbela on ke…ďii fodoore Alla te Alla luutndotaako aadi Makko wolla ngon-…óon ko haalde e Alla ko on nganndanaa
  2,81,"Ko goonga kala mbo faggitii bonannde bon…ói makko piilii mo, ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe jayngol luttoo…ďe toon"
  2,82,∆Āeen goon…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īereeji ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe aljanna luttoo…ďe toon
  2,83,Min …ďamii fodoore e …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla mo∆ī∆īon e jibnaa…ďe e jiidaa…ďe e waay…óu…ďe e waas…ďe o…óon kaalana yim…ďe …ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi darnon juulde tottiron asakal …ďaawo …óuum cali-…óon …óuurni-…óon sonaa see…óa e moo…óon
  2,84,Nde Min ∆īetti fodoore mon wota on nduf ∆īii∆īe mon taa on njaltin ko'e mon galleeji mon …ói ndeen nja…ď-…óon ceedi…óon …óum
  2,85,"Rewi heen onon …ďee o…óon mbara ko'e mon o…óon njaltina yim…ďe e mon galleeji ma…ď…ďe, o…óon pe√Ī√Īina too√Īe mon e ma…ď…ďe, si …ďe arii e mon dahaa…ďe coodtidon…ďe yaltingol …ďe na harmi e mon, mbela on goon…óinat yoga e deftere nde njeddon yoga heen kala e mon wa…óoo…ďe …óum njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ko koyeera weejo aduna √Īande darnga …ďe nduttee e lette …ďur…óe bonde Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,86,∆Āeen soodir…ďe laakara nguurndam aduna …ďe koynantaake lette …ďe ke…ďataa ballo
  2,87,Min ngaddanii Muusaa deftere nde …ďaawo makko Min ndewni heen nulaa…ďe Min ngaddani Iisaa …ďii Maryam la…ď…ďinale Min cemmbirini mo wonki tedduki mbela kala nde nulaa…óo addi he mon ko welaani pittaali mon mawnikino-…óon yoga heen njeddon …ďe yoga heen mbaron …ďe
  2,88,"∆Āe mbii …ďer…óe amen …óe ko uddii…óe, accu tan ko Alla hu…ói …ďe sabu keefeeru ma…ď…ďe, na fam…ói ko …ďe ngoon…óinta"
  2,89,"Nde deftere ari e ma…ď…ďe iwde e Alla, ende nuun…óina ko …ďe njogii ado …óuum …ďe ngonndoo ko wallitoraade …óum dow …ďeen yeddu…ďe nde ko …ďe nganndi ko ari he ma…ď…ďe …ďe njiddi …óum, yo ku…ódi Alla won e heefer…ďe"
  2,90,Bone woni e ko…ďe coodiri ko'e ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe njeddi -e too√Īe- ko Alla jippini Alla jippinta …ďural Makko dow mbo O welaa e jeyaa…ďe Mako …ďe kaandii e tikkere mawnde heefer…ďe …ďee na ke…ďa lette bon…óe
  2,91,"Si …ďe mbi'aama ngoon…óinee ko Alla jippini ko …ďe mbi'a min ngoon…óina ko jippinaa e amen …ďe njedda ko wonaa …óuum te ko …óuum woni goonga nuun…óin…óo ko …ďe njogii, wii …ďe ko wa…ói o…óon mbarannoo annabaa…ďe Alla …ďe so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini"
  2,92,Nde Muusaa addani on la…ď…ďinale njogiti-…óon ngaari ndi …ďaawo makko onon ko on too√Īoo…ďe
  2,93,"Min …ďami e mon fodoore Min …ďamti dow mon haayre Tuur ∆īettiree ko Min ngaddani on ko e semmbe nanee, …ďe mbii min nanii min ngoopi …ďer…óe mum en …óe keewi dak rewde ngaari ndi e keefeeru ma…ď…ďe, wii bone wonii e ko goon…óingol mon yamiri on so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini"
  2,94,Wii so tawii ko onon tan ke…ďata aljanna to laakara njelo…óee maayde so tawii ko on goon…óu…ďe
  2,95,∆Āe njelotaako …óum pooma e ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe ngardini Alla Ombo anndi too√Īoo…ďe …ďe
  2,96,Maa a taw ko kam…ďe …ďuri reer…óude e nguurndam e …ďeen renndin…ďe e Alla mbela gooto e ma…ď…ďe na yi…ói wuurde duu…ďe ujunere wuurde mbo ko juuti wo…ó…óintaa mo lette Alla Mo yi'a golle ma…ď…ďe
  2,97,Wii kala gon…óo ga√Īo Jibriil yo anndu ko kanko yottini Kur'aana nder …ďernde maa e yamiroore Alla nde nuun…óini defte …óe …ďe njogii ko nde peewal e malu goon…óin…ďe
  2,98,Kala gon…óo ga√Īo Alla e malaykaa…ďe Makko e nulaa…ďe Makko e Jibriil e Miika'il Alla dey ko ga√Īo heefer…ďe …ďe
  2,99,Min njippinii e maa maandeeji la…ď…ďinooji alaa jeddoowo …ói sonaa faasigee…ďe …ďe
  2,100,Wolla kala nde …ďe pi…ďi aadi wooda e ma…ď…ďe firtu…ďe mbo accu tan …ďur…ďe heewde e ma…ď…ďe ngoon…óinaani
  2,101,"Nde Nulaa…óo Alla ari e ma…ď…ďe ombo goon…óina ko …ďe njogii ko, woodi heen sete salii rontii deftere Alla nde wa'i no …ďe nganndaa nii"
  2,102,"∆Āe ndewi ko sey…óaneeji njannganta laamu Suleymaan Suleymaan yeddaani kono ko sey…óaneeji …ói njeddi e…ói nganndina yim…ďe mbilewu e ko jippina dow malaykaa…ďe …ói…óo to Baabil e Haaruut e Maaruu kala nde …ďe nganndini go…ó…óo …ďe mbi'a minen dey ko min fitina taa yeddu, …ďe jnnga e ma…ď…ďe no …ďe ceerndirta neddo e debbo mum, …ďe lorataa hay gooto sinaa e yamiroore Alla …ďe njannga ko bonnanta …ďe, …ďe nganndii kala battindir…óo …óum alaa ge…óal to laakara ko bone …ďe mbattiti ko'e ma…ď…ďe tawiino …ďe nganndi"
  2,103,Tawno …ďe ngoon…óinii …ďe kuli Alla ko mbarjaari immorde e Alla …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude
  2,104,"Onon goon…óin…ďe taa mbi'ee aynu min mbi'ee ndaar (fadir) min nanee, heefer…ďe …ďee na ke…ďa lette. muus…óe"
  2,105,"∆Āeen yim…ďe deftere yeddu…ďe e renndin…ďe e Alla nji…óataa jooma mon jippina e mon mo∆ī∆ī ere,Alla noon ko MboO welaa o wa…óanta yurmeend e Mum ko O jooma …ďural mawngal"
  2,106,Kala nde Min itti aaye maa momti mbo deen Min ngadda …ďur…óo mbo maa wano mbo mbela a anndaa Alla Mo waawi kala huunde
  2,107,Mbela a anndaa wonde ko Alla jeyi laamu asamaanji e lesdi on ngalaa keedanoowo mon wolla ballo sonaa Alla
  2,108,"Wolla nji…ó-…óon ko naamnaade nulaa…óo mon o wano Muusaa naamnoranoo ko adi,i kala mbo wattiti goon…óingol keefeeru tawa o majjii laawol peewngol"
  2,109,Heew…ďe e yim…ďe deftere nji…ói ruttude on heefer…ďe …ďaawo goon…óingol mon ko nga√Īgu pittaali mum en caggal nde …ďe laa…ďaa goonga o njaafee ngaccanon haa yamiroore Alla ara Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde
  2,110,√Ďii…ďnee juulde tottiree asakal kala mo∆ī∆īere nde mba…óan-…óon ko'e mon maa on tawnde to Alla ko Kanko Alla woni ji'oowo ko ngolloton
  2,111,"∆Āe mbii alaa naatoowo aljanna sonaa Yahuude maa nasaaraajo …óuum woni muuyaande ma…ď…ďe, wii: …ďe ngaddee daliil moo…óon so tawii ko on goon…óu…ďe"
  2,112,"Ko goonga kala mbo totti yeeso makko Alla o woni mo∆ī∆īini, ma o he…ó mbarjaari makko to joomum kulol alanaa …ďe …ďe cunotaako"
  2,113,"Yahuud en mbii nasaara en ngonaani e hay huunde nasaara en mbii yahuud en ngonaani e hay huunde, tawa e…ďe njannga deftere nde, ko noon …ďe nganndaa …ďe mbiinoo ko Alla √Īaawata luural hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Īande darnga"
  2,114,"Hombo …ďuri too√Īe oon ka…óoowo yo innde Alla jante nder juulir…óe ombo daranii bonnude …óe …ďeen potaani naatde …óe so wonaa e kulol, …ďe ke…ďa koyeera e aduna …ďe ke…ďa lette maw…óe to laakara"
  2,115,"Fu…ónaange e hirnaange ko Alla woodani kala heen …óo kuccit, toon ko yeeso Alla, pellet Alla noon ko jaaj…óo e ganngal Makko piiltingal"
  2,116,"∆Āe mbii Alla Mo jogitii …ďi…ó…óo senaande woodanii Mo, nganndee kala ko woni e asamaanji e lesdi ko Kanko woodani fof na …óoftoo Mo"
  2,117,"Pu…ó…óu…óo asamaanji …ói e lesdi ndi, so O √Īaawii huunde O wi'ata …óum tan ko: won …óum wona"
  2,118,"∆Āe nganndaa …ďe mbi'a mbela Alla haaldataa min wolla O addana min maande, ko noon adinoo…ďe ma…ď…ďe mbiinoo …ďer…óe mum en nanndi goonga tigi Min la…ď…ďinii maandeeji …ói wonande yim…ďe yananaa…ďe …ďe"
  2,119,"Minen Min nelirii ma goonga ngonaa beltinoowo jeertinoowo, A naa…ďntaake ma yim…ďe jayngol Jahannama"
  2,120,Yahuud e nasaara en mbeletaake ma haa njokkaa laawol ma…ď…ďe yo a wii …ďe nganndee ko peewal Alla woni peewal so a jokkii belee…óe ma…ď…ďe …ďaawo nde ke…ď…óaa ganndal ndeen a da√Īataa ballal Alla
  2,121,"∆Āeen …ďe Min ngaddani deftere nde e…ďe nde njannga no haaniri ko …ďeen tigi ngoon…óini nde, kala mbo yeddi nde ko …ďeen tigi ngoni bonnoraa…ďe"
  2,122,"Onon …ďi…ď…ďe Isra'iil ciftoree mo∆ī∆īereeji Am …ói Mi wa…óani on, Miin tigi wa…ói mon …ďurir…óon winndere"
  2,123,"Kulee √Īande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittandu wonndu te ndu ja…ďantaake coodtiigu kadi tefaneede nafataa ndu, …ďe ke…ďataa ballo"
  2,124,"Nde Alla humpitori Ibrahiima konngi o timmini …ói, O Wi'i: Miin Mi wa…óat ma gardotoo…óo yim…ďe …ďe Ibarahiima wi'i wa…ó …óum kadi e …ďesngu am O wi'i too√Īoo…ďe …ďe ke…ďataa fodoore Am"
  2,125,Nde Min mba…ói suudu ndu ruttorde yim…ďe e hoolaare njokito-…óee darnde Ibrahiima wona juulirde Min ngaadanii Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iila yo …ďe la…ď…ďin suudu Amngam wanngotoo…ďe e ufnotoo…ďe e juuloo…ďe
  2,126,Nde Ibrahiima wi'i jooma am wa…óan min nduu suudu leydi hoolniindi nje…óaa yim…ďe mum …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe wonande goon…óin…ďe Alla e √Īande wattan O wi'i kala jeddu…óo Mi weltina mo see…óa fawoo heen Mi faana mon lette jayngol e battane bon…óe
  2,127,Nde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila …ďamtatnoo dos…óe suudu ndu e…ďe mbi'a Jooma amen ja…ďan min ko Aan woni nanoowo nganndu…óo fof
  2,128,Jooma amen wa…ó min ja…ďan…ďe Ma mba…óaa e …ďesngu amen le√Īol juul…ďe yo A hollu min tinndinor…óe dewe amen njaafo-∆äaa min ko Aan tigi woni jaafotoo…óo jurmotoo…óo
  2,129,"Jooma amen wa…ó e ma…ď…ďe nulaa…óo ombo janngana …ďe aayeeje Maa o anndina …ďe Kur'aana Maa o e sunna o, o la…ď…ďina …ďe ko Aaan tigi woni jaalii…óo √Īee√Ī…óu…óo"
  2,130,Alaa …óuurnotoo…óo (calotoo…óo) laawol Ibrahiima sonaa mbo fittaandu mum …óaayi nganndee Min cu…ďiima mo e aduna kanko o jeyaa ko e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe to laakara
  2,131,Nde Jooma mum wii Mo ja…ďanAm ngonaa juul…óo o wi'i mi ja…ďanii Jooma binnde …óe
  2,132,"Ibrahiima tinndini …ďi…ď…ďe mum, Yaakuub kadi wa…ói noon, onon …ďi…ď…ďe am Alla su…ďaniima on diine …óe taa maayee sonaa ko on juul…ďe"
  2,133,Mbela on ceediima nde maayde arani Yaakuuba nde o wii …ďi…ď…ďe mum …ďee holko ndewoton caggal am…ďe mbii min ndewan dewetee…óo maa e dewetee…óo baabiraa…ďe maa Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak dewetee…óo gooto minen ko oon min njebbilanii
  2,134,"Ngool ko le√Īol jawtungol engol he…ďa ko ngol fagginoo, onon ne o…óon ke…ďa ko paggi-…óon on naamnetaake ko …ďe ngollatnoo"
  2,135,"Yahuud e Nasaara en mbii ngonee Yahuuda maa Nasaara ndeen peewon wii: -aan annabiijo- accu dey min ngonata ko e diine Ibrahiima peew…ó …óe o jeyanooka e sirku…ďe …ďe"
  2,136,Mbi'ee min ngoon…óinii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaak e Yaakuub e Asbaat e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e ko annabaa…ďe …ďee okka iwde e joomiraawo ma…ď…ďe min ceerndataa hay gooto e ma…ď…ďe ko kam…ďe min njebbilanii
  2,137,So tawii …ďe ngoon…óinii wano ko ngoon…óin-…óon ko ndeen tawa …ďe peewii so …ďe …óuurniima ndeen …ďe ngoni ko e luutndaade maa Alla suran ma …ďe ko Kanko woni nanoowo nganndu…óo fof
  2,138,"Diine Alla neesuyaŇčkooje alaa diine baa…óe no diine Alla …óe, minen ko Kanko min ndewata"
  2,139,"Wii mbela on njeddondirat e amen fii Alla te ko Kanko woni joomiroowo men, min ke…ďat golle amen ke…ďon golle mon minen ko Kanko min laa…ďanta"
  2,140,"Mbela on nji…ó wiide wonde Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaka e Yaakuub e Asbaat …ďe ngonndoo ko yahudee…ďe maa nasaara…ďe, wii mbela ko onon …ďuri anndude Alla hol mbo …ďuri too√Īe oon cuu…óoowo seedanfaagu iwde e Alla, Alla noon yeebotaako ko …ďe ngollata ko"
  2,141,"Ngool ko le√Īol jawtungol engol he…ďa ko ngol, fagginoo onon ne o…óon ke…ďa ko paggi-…óon on naamnetaake ko …ďe ngollatnoo"
  2,142,"Arma ka …ďe fuyunngaa…ďe e yim…ďe mbi'a: \"E ko hucciŇčtini …ďe ga'e Qibla ma…ď…ďe mo …ďe laatinoo e mu'un?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla Woodani fu…ónaange e hiirnaange, Himo Fewnira on Mo O Muuyi faade laawol focciingol"
  2,143,"Ko wano nii Men wa…óiri on mofte hakindii…óe fii yo on laato seedoytoo…ďe e dow yim…ďe …ďen, Nulaa…óo on seeditoyoo e dow mo'on. Men wa…óiraa oo Qibla mo fewtataa e mu'un si wanaa no Men anndira on jokkoowo Nulaa…óo on e on ruttotoo…óo batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii …óum laatike ko sattu-…óum, si wanaa e dow …ďen …ďe Allah fewni. Allah Laatoraali yeeboowo liimanaaku mo'on: Pellet, Allah ko Hilnotoo…óo yim…ďe …ďen Yurmee …ďe"
  2,144,"Gom…óii Me…óen Reeni waylitorgol yeeso maa ngon ka kammu. Ma Men Fewtinire Qibla waalaŇčtoo…óo ma:Fewtinir yeeso maa…óa ngon baŇčŇče Juulirde HoormaŇčteere nden.Nokku kala ko ngo…óon,fewtiniree geece mon …óen baŇčŇče mayru:Pellet,…ďen Rokkaa…ďe Defte …ďen no anndi [Al Qur'aanaare nden] ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe,Allah non siforaali Welsinsii…óo e ko …ďe gollata"
  2,145,"Mi Woondii si a addanii …ďen rokkaa…ďe deftere nden kala maande,…ďe jokkataa Qibla maa on,a wonaa jokkoowo Qibla ma…ď…ďe on,yoga e ma…ď…ďe wonaali jokkoo…ďe Qibla yoga.Mi Woondii si a jokkii m…ďelee…óe maa…ďe …ďaawo kon ko ari e maa e anndal,pellet,an ontuma a jeyaama e too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  2,146,"∆Āen …ďe Men Rokki Deftere nden hi…ďe nganndiri …óum wano …ďe nganndiri …ďi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe; pellete, fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe hino suu…óude goonga kan hara hi…ďe nganndi"
  2,147,"Goonga kan ko ko ummori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e …ďen sikkitii…ďe"
  2,148,"Ena woodani mo kala baŇčŇče …óe o fewtata e mun.Adondiree e mo∆ī∆īereeji,nokku kala ka laati-…óon,Allah artiray on,on denndaangal. Pellete,Allah ko hattan…óo e dow kala huunde"
  2,149,"Nokku kala ka yaltir…óaa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baŇčŇče Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, pellet, …óum ko goonga ummoraade Joomi maa, Allah Wonaali Welsindii…óo e kon ko gollo-ton"
  2,150,"Nokku kala ka yaltir…óaa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baŇčŇče Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, nokku kala ka ngon…óon, fewtiniree geece mon …óen baŇčŇče mayru fii wata wonan yim…ďe …ďen hujja e hoore mo'on - so wanaa …ďen too√Īu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Wata non on hulu…ďe, Hulee Lam, fii no Mi Timminira neema Am On e mo'on, belajo'o on feeway"
  2,151,"Wano no Men Nuliri non e mo'on Nulaa…óo ummoraade e mo'on,Himo janngana on Aayeeje Amen,himo la…ď…ďina on,himo anndina on Deftere nden,o anndina on ko on anndaana"
  2,152,"JaŇčtee Lam, Mi Anndita on; jaarnee Lam wata on yeddam"
  2,153,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe, wallitoree mu√Ī√Īaare e juulde. Pellet, Allah Hino Wonndi e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen"
  2,154,"Wata on wi'an …ďen wariraa…ďe fii Allah …ďen: \"ko …ďe maay…ďe\". Ko woni, …ďen ko wuur…ďe, kono on so'aa anndude"
  2,155,"Ma Men jaribo on huunde, immorde e kulol, e heege, e …óuytagol jawle, e woŇčkiiji, e dim…óe; Wewlin mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen"
  2,156,"∆Āen taw…ďe si masiibo he…ďii…ďe, …ďe wi'a: \"Menen dey ko Allah jeyi men, pellet to Makko menruttortoo"
  2,157,"∆Āen …óon, hino e dow ma…ď…ďe toraaje e yurmeende ummoraade ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko kam…ďe ngoni feewu…ďe …ďen"
  2,158,"Pellet,Safaa e Marwa ko jeyaa…óe e maandeeji [diine] Allah.Kala on hajju…óo ka suudu [Kaaba], maa o wa…ói Umra,ella woo fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji.On mo gattii mo∆ī∆īere,pellet Allah ko Jaarnoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,159,"Pellet, …ďen suudoo…ďe kon ko Men Jippini immorde e …ďanngannduyeeji e peewal, …ďaawo nde Men ∆Āannginani …óum yim…ďe …ďen ka Deftere, …ďen …óon, Allah ena Hu…óude …ďe, hu…óoo…ďe …ďen na hu…óude …ďe"
  2,160,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďe mo∆ī∆īini …ďe …ďaŇčngini: Mi Ja…ďanay …ďen …óon tuubuubuyee, ko Min Woni Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,161,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi ko …ďe heereraa…ďe, …ďen …óon ena fawii…ďe kuddi Allah ndin e Malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďen denndaangal"
  2,162,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe e magge. ∆Āe hayfinaŇčtaake le…ďte …óen, …ďe wonaali nennanaŇčtee…ďe"
  2,163,"Rewetee…óe mon On ko Rewetee…óe Gooto. Rewetee…óo Alaa tanaa Makko, Jurmotoo…óo Yurmeende heeriinde e nde heeraaki Yurmeende"
  2,164,"Pellet hino e ndeer tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e luutondiral jemma e √Īalorma on, e le…ó…óe dogirooje …óen ka bahru nafugol yim…ďe …ďen, e kon ko Allah Jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e ndiyam, O Wurniri …óum leydi ndin …ďaawo maayugol mayri O Saakti e mayri kala daaba, e waylitugol keneeli …óin e duule eltaa…óe …óen hakkunde leydi e kammu, maandeeji wonannde yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe"
  2,165,"Hino e yim…ďe njogitii…ďe ko woori Allah yerondir…ói, hi…ďe nji…óira…ói wano Allah yi…óirtee, [ko] …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďuri sa…ótude giggol wonande Allah. Hara …ďen too√Īu…ďe annduno tuma …ďe nji'oyta lepte …óen, wonde doole …óen fof ko Allah heeranii, e wonde Allah ko Sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  2,166,"Tuma nde hisnii jokkanoo…ďe …ďen pottitoyii jokkunoo…ďe …ďen, …ďe nji'a lepte …óen, sabuuji …óin ta∆īira …ďe"
  2,167,"Jokkunoo…ďe …ďen mbi'a: \"Hara nun fehre ruttagol no woodannoo men, men pottitora …ďe wano …ďe pottitori men nii\". Ko wano nii Allah Hollirta …ďe golleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin; hayrere e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ngonaali njaltoo…ďe e yiite ngen"
  2,168,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe! √Ďaamee yoga e ko woni ka leydi ko dagii ko laa…ďi, wata on jokku juri=taabe seytaane …óin : Pellet, ko o ga√Īo mo'on fee√Īu…óo"
  2,169,"Anndee ko o yamirta on ko bone e paŇčkare, e nde wowloton e hoore Allah ko on anndaa"
  2,170,"Si …ďe wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", …ďe mbi'a:\"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraa…ďe amen\";e hay si baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen haqqilataa hay e huunde …ďe haanditaaki"
  2,171,"Misal …ďen yeddu…ďe hino wa'i wa on ewnotoo…óo kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko faa…óu…ói, mumi…óu…ói, wumu…ói; kaŇčji …ói haqqiltaa"
  2,172,"Ko onon yo …ďen gom…óim…ďe! √Ďamee immorde e laa…ďu…ói …ói Men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko KaŇčko rewoton"
  2,173,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jii…ďe, e ∆īii∆īam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on du√Īaa…óo [e √Īaamugol …óum] hara wanaa …ďew…óo wanaa jaggitu…óo, bakkatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko Ya'fotoo…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  2,174,"Pellet …ďen suu…óoo…ďe ko Allah Jippini kon e Deftere nden, hi…ďe soodira …óum cogguwel fam…óungel. ∆Āen …óon alaa wa…óude ka deedi ma…ď…ďe si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah Yeewtidtaa …ďe √Īalnde darngal, O La…ď…ďiŇčtaa …ďe, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  2,175,"Ko …ďen ngoni soodir…ďe majjere nden peewal, e lepte …óen ya'fuyee. kaawse ko mu√Ī√Īori…ďe ka yiite"
  2,176,"∆äuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii Deftere nden goonga. pellet …ďen luutondir…ďe e Deftere nden …ďe ngonii e lurral wo…ó…óungal"
  2,177,"Dewal ngal wonaali fewtiŇčgol geece mon …óen …ďaŇčnge fu…ónaange e hiirnaange. Ko woni tun dewal ngal: ko on gom…óin…óo Alla e √Ďalaande sakkitiinde nden, e Malaa'ika en, e Deftere nden, e Annabaa…ďe …ďen; o okki jawdi -e hoore yi…óugol ndi- joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral, e wondu…ďe …ďen, e …ďillii…ďe …ďen, e …ďii hoore-laawol, e …ďen torotoo…ďe, e fii rin…óinngol daa…óe; o nii…ďni juulde, o totti asakal, e …ďen hunnoo…ďe aadondiral ma…ď…ďe si …ďe haldidaama, e …ďen mu√Ī√Īitoo…ďe ka baasi e ka lorra, e fewndo gowole. Ko …ďen ngoni goongu…ďe …ďen, ko …ďen kadi ngoni gom…óu…ďe"
  2,178,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe,njottiigu farlaama e mo'on:dimo sabu dimo, jeyaa…óo sabu jeyaa…óo,deyel sabu deyel.Kala ya'fanaa…óo go…ó…óum e musi…ó…óo makko,ko jokkitirogol no mo∆ī∆īiri tottira e makko no mo∆ī∆īiri.∆äum …óoo ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on e yurmeende.Kala on jaggitu…óo …ďaawo …óu'um,no woodani mo lepte muusu…óe"
  2,179,"No woodani on ka njottiigu nguurdam, yo joomiraa…ďe haqqilaaji. Belajo'o on wonay gom…óu…ďe"
  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on:si maayde nden arii e mo'on,si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibin…ďe mo …ďen,e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen no mo∆ī∆īiri.Ko hannduyee e dow gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  2,181,"Kala on waylitu…óo …óum …ďaawo o nannde, pellet bakkaatu mun on ko …ďen waylitu…ďe fawii. Allah ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,182,"On mo huli oo√Īaare immorde e wasiyii…óo maa bakkaatu o mo∆ī∆īini hakkunde ma…ď…ďe,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko Yawtanoowo Yurmotoo…óo"
  2,183,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, koorka kan farlaama e mo'on wano ka farliranoo e …ďen adinoo…ďe on, …ďelajo'o laato…óon gom…óu…ďe"
  2,184,"√Ďal…ói limtaa…ói. Kala e mo'on laatii…óo nawnu…óo maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol √Īal…ói goo. No fawii …ďen ha…ótan…ďe ka, √Īammingol …ďilii…óo. Kala on gattu…óo mo∆ī∆īere …óum no mo∆ī∆īani mo. Ko nde hooroton …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on, si wonii hi…óon nganndi"
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa e mu'un, ko ndu peewal wonannde yim…ďe …ďen e …ďangannduyeeji immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on seedii…óo lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On taw…óo no nawni maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e √Īal…ói goo. Alla no Faandanii on neweende O Faandanaaki on sa…óteende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawniniro Alla kon ko O Fewni on, belajo'o on jaarnay Mo"
  2,186,"Si jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen lamndike lan fii Am, hary Min: Ko Mi ∆Āa…óii…óo. Mi…óo Jaabina toraare torotoo…óo si o torike Lam. Yo …ďe nooto Lam, e yo …ďe gom…óinam, belajo'o …ďe feeway"
  2,187,"Daginanaama on jemma koorka kan yiidugol e rew…ďe mon …ďen. Ko …ďe koltu mo'on ko on koltu ma…ď…ďe. Alla Anndii wonde on laatinoke jaŇčfotoo…ďe ko*e-mon,O Ja…ďani on tuubuubuyee O Ya'fii on.Jooni non,soccondiree e ma…ď…ďe …óa…ď…ďon ko Alla Winndani on.√Ďaamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol …ďaŇčngirana on …ďalewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e ma…ď…ďe hara ko on ufnii…ďe ka juulir…óe.∆äum ko keeri Allah, wata on …ďa…óto …ói.Ko wano nii Allaahu On ∆ĀaŇčnginiraŇčta yim…ďe …ďen aayeeje Makko …óen,belajo'o …ďe wona gom…óu…ďe"
  2,188,"Wata on √Īaamir jawle mon …óen hakkundeeji mo'on e hoore mehre, werloron …óe e √Īaawoo…ďe …ďen fii yo fedde goo √Īaamira e jawle yim…ďe …ďen bakkaatu, hara hi…óon nganndi"
  2,189,"Hi…ďe naamno-maa fii daror…óe lebbi, wi'u: \"∆äin ko waqaŇčtinanay…ói yim…ďe e fii hajju\".Dewal ngal wonaali nde ngardaŇčton cuu…ói …óin immorde ka …ďabbe majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on gom…óu…óo.Ngardanee cuu…ói …óin ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belajo'o on malete"
  2,190,"Ha…ďee fii laawol Alla ngol …ďen ha…ďoo…ďe on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla yi…óaa jaggitoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,191,"waree…ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe, yaltinee…ďe nokku ka …ďe yaltiniri on: ko geddi …óin …ďuri mawnude e dii ha…ďugol ngol. Wata on ha…ďu…ďe ka Misiide HormaŇčteere haa …ďe ha…ďa on e mayre. Si …ďe ha…ďii on ha…ďee …ďe. Ko wano nii woni njo…ďdi heefer…ďe …ďen"
  2,192,"Si …ďe ha…óitike, pellet, Alla ko O Hafroowo Huu…ďu…óo-yumeende"
  2,193,"Ha…ďee …ďe haa nokku ka laatotaako fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si …ďe ha…óitike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa …ďen too√Īoo…ďe"
  2,194,"Si …ďe ha…ďii on e lewru hormaŇčteeru, ha…ďee …ďe e lewru hormaŇčteeru, horminaa…ói …óin ko yottondirtee …óum. On mo jaggiti e mo'on jaggitee e dow makko yeru kon ko o jaggiti e dow moo…óon. Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wonndi …ďen gom…óu…ďe"
  2,195,"WiŇčtee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juu…óe mon …óen faade e halakuyee. Mo∆ī∆īinee, pellet Alla no Yi…ói mo∆ī∆īinay…ďe …ďen"
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju ngun e 'omra on fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon …óen haa kirse …óen yottoo nokku majje. On taw…óo e mo'on ko √Īaw…óo maa lorra no ka hoore makko, ko soktorgol: koorka, maa sadaqa maa dammol. Si on wonii e hoolaare, on mo dakmitori 'omra on haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol kon ko newii e kirse. Mo he…ďaali, ko hoorugol bal…óe tati ka hajju e jee…ói…ói si on ruttike; …óen ko sappo timmu…óe. Ko jaŇčtaa koo, ko fii on taw…óo …ďeynguure mun nden laataaki ho…óu…ďe ka Misiide hormaŇčte. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaa…ói. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollug…óon e mo∆ī∆īere, Allah no Anndi …óum.Yoo…ďee,ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e njoo…ďa,ko gom…óal. Hulee Lam yo joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde …óa…ď…ďoton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaŇčtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. JaŇčtoron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muu…óum ko on jeyaa…ďe e majju…ďe"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yim…ďe …ďen yahri …óon, Insinano…óon Alla. Pellet Alla ko Yaafotoo…óo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, jaŇčtoree innde Alla wano jaŇčtorton baabiraa…ďe mo'on, maa ko …ďuri …óum tii…óude. No e yim…ďe …ďen wi'oo…ďe: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara ge…ďal-mo∆ī∆īal"
  2,201,"No e ma…ď…ďe wi'oo…ďe: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe ge…ďal-mo∆ī∆īal e kon ko …ďe faggitii. Alla ko Yaawu…óo hasboore"
  2,203,"JaŇčtee Innde Alla e √Īal…ói limtaa…ói. On yaccin…óo e nder bal…óe …ói…ói, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on ne…ďtin…óo kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonannde on gom…óu…óo. Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet ko ka Makko moo…ďindiroyte-…óon"
  2,204,"No e yim…ďe …ďen on mo konngol mun no haawne ka nguurdam aduna, himo seediŇčtina Alla kon ko woni e ndeer …ďernde makko, hara non ko kaŇčko …ďuri sa…ótude wennje"
  2,205,"Si o huccitii, o yaha ka leydi fii o bonnu e mayri, o halka gese e ge√Ī√Īi. Alla Yi…óaa bononda"
  2,206,"Si o wi'anaama: \"Hulu Alla\", mawniŇčtinaare he…ďa mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii nda…ó…óudi"
  2,207,"No e yim…ďe …ďen: on mo no soo…ótira woŇčkii mun kin …óa…ď…ďugol yarluyee Alla. Alla ko Hilnotoo…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  2,208,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, naatiree e lislaamu ka denndanngal, wata on jokku juri seytaane …óin. On ko ga√Īo moo…óon …ďaŇčngu…óo"
  2,209,"Si on oo√Īike …ďaawo koo ko ari on e …ďaŇčngannduyeeji, nganndee pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,210,"Taw si …ďee no sabbii: si wanaa nde Allaahu On ArdaŇčta …ďe e ndeer ni…ďe duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku gasinee. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  2,211,"Naamno ge…óal…ďe Israa'iila en:ko jelu woni ko Men Rokki …ďe e maandeeji …ďaŇčngu…ói! Kala wa…ótitu…óo neema Alla on …ďaawo on arude mo, pellet, Alla ko Tii…óu…óo lepte"
  2,212,"Nguurdam aduna …óam cu…óinanaama …ďeya heefer…ďe, hi…ďe jalkita …ďen gom…óim…ďe. ∆Āen gom…óu…ďe wonoyay dow ma…ď…ďe √Īalnde darngal. Alla no Arsikira on Mo O Muuyi, ko aldaa e hasboore"
  2,213,"Yim…ďe …ďen laatino mofte goote. Allaahu On Nuli Annabaa…ďe …ďen, wewlinoo…ďe e jeertinoo…ďe, O Jippindini e ma…ď…ďe Deftere nden hoore goonga, fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen kon ko …ďe luuondiri e muu…óum. Luutondiraali e muu…óum, si wanaa …ďen rokkaa…ďe nde, …ďaawo kon ko ari …ďe e …ďaŇčngannduyeeji; ka bewre hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Allah Fewniri duŇčyee Makko …ďen gom…óim…ďe e kon ko …ďe luutondiri e muu…óum, immorde e goonga. Alla No Fewna on Mo O Muuyi, faade e laawol focciingol"
  2,214,"Kaa on sikku on naatay aljanna hara araali on sugu kon ko arunoo …ďen wulii…ďe on? He…ďiino …ďen sa…ótteende e lorra, …ďe dillinaa haa Nulaa…óo wi'i, e …ďen gom…óindim…ďe e makko: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ballal Alla ngal?\", hey, pellte ballal Alla ngal …ďa…ótiingal"
  2,215,"∆Āe ngaray naamnaade ma ko hon…óum …ďe sakkotoo, wi'u: \"Si won ko sakki…óon e mo∆ī∆īere, ko fii jibin…ďe on, e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen, e wondu…ďe …ďen, e …ďilii…ďe …ďen, e setee…ďe …ďen. kalako gollu…óon e mo∆ī∆īere, pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo …óum"
  2,216,"Hare nden farlaama e mo'on; nden non ko a√Īaande e mo'on,no tijjaa ka a√Īoton huunde hara ko nde mo∆ī∆īere mon, no tijjaa kadi ka yi…óoton huunde hara ko nde bone mon. Ko Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,217,"Hi…ďe naamno maa fii lewru hormaŇčte ndun, ha…ďugol e mayru, maaku: \"Ha…ďugol e mayru ko mawnu-…óum. Ko sakkagol e laawol Alla ngol e yeddugol Mo e Misiide hormorde nden e yaltingol yim…ďe mayre …ďen e mayre, …ďuri mawnude ka Alla. Ko shirku on kadi …ďuri mawnude dii wargol ngol; …ďe seerataa hi…ďe ha…ďa on haa …ďe rutta on e diina mon, si …ďe haa…ótanii. Kala e mo'on yaltondir…óo e diina mu'un, o maayi ko o keefeero: …ďen …óon, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen bonii aduna e laakara; ko …ďen ngoni yim…ďe yiite, …ďen ko luttoo…ďe ton"
  2,218,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe e …ďen feru…ďe ha…ďiri fii laawol Alla, …ďen …óon no jortii Yurmeende Alla; Alla ko Ya'fotoo…óo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,219,"Hi…ďe naamno-maa fi sanngara e karte, maaku: \"No e …óin …ói…ói bakkaatu maw…óo e nafawoy wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, ko bakkaatu majji on non …ďuri mawnude e dii nafawoy majji on\". Hi…ďe naamno-maa kadi hol ko …ďe sakkotoo? Maaku: \"yaafuya=Ko fawi e haaju\". Ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀaŇčnginiraŇčta on Aayeeje …óen, belajo'o on miijitoto"
  2,220,"Fii aduna on e laakara on, hi…ďe naamno-maa fii wondu…ďe …ďen, maaku: \"Ko mo∆ī∆īagol e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude\". Si on jillondirii e ma…ď…ďe, ko musi…ó…ďe mo'on. Alla no Anndi on mo∆ī∆īinoowo e on bonnoowo. Si Alla muuyuno, O ∆Āi…ótinanayno on. Pellet Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,221,"Wata on resu …ďen rew…ďe shirkay…ďe haa …ďe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko kor…óo gom…óin…óo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude debbo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. Wata on resin …ďen wor…ďe shirkoo…ďe haa …ďe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko maccu…óo gom…óin…óo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.∆Āen …óon hi…ďe nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e duŇčyee Makko. Himo ∆ĀaŇčngina Aayeeje Makko …óen wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, belajo'o …ďe wa'ajitoto"
  2,222,"Hi…ďe naam-no maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ∆äum ko nefinii …óum; luncitee rew…ďe …ďen fewndo fiilordu, wata on …ďa…óto …ďe haa …ďe laa…ďa. Si …ďe laa…ďii, ngaree e ma…ď…ďe nokku ka Alla Yamiri on …óon. Pellet Alla No Yi…ói tuubaya…ďe …ďen Himo Yi…ói kadi …ďen la…ď…ďinotoo…ďe"
  2,223,"Rew…ďe mon …ďen ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faalira…óon, ngardinanee woŇčkiiji mon …óin. Hulle Alla, nganndon ko on kawroo…ďe e Makko. Weltin gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  2,224,"Wata on wa…óu Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon …óen; nde …óiggoton, gom…óon hulon mo∆ī∆īinon hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko …ďer…óe mon …óen faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  2,226,"No woodani …ďen woondiroo…ďe suddii…ďe mun …ďen: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si …ďe ruttike, pellet Alla ko Haforoowo Huu…ďu…óo-yurmeende"
  2,227,"Si …ďe fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,228,"Seeraa…ďe …ďen yo habbiŇčtin ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen laa…ďe tati; dagaŇčtaako …ďe suu…óugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji ma…ď…ďe, si wonii hi…ďe gom…óim…ďe Alla e √Īalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe jojjidi ruttugol …ďe e …óum, si hawrii hi…ďe faalaa weldital. No woodani …ďen [rew…ďe] yeru kon ko fawii…ďe, no mo∆ī∆īiri. No woodani wor…ďe …ďen: …ďural e dow ma…ď…ďe. Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,229,"Ceergal, ko laa…ďi …ói…ó: ko jogitorgol no mo∆ī∆īiri maa accitira no mo∆ī∆īiri. DagaŇčtaako on ∆īettitugol huunde e kon ko rokku-…óon …ďe, si wanaa hara …ďe hulii [kam…ďe …ói…óo] nde …ďe nii…ďnataa keeri Alla …óin. Si on hulii roŇčkude √Īii…ďnude keeri Alla …óin, goopi alanaa …ďe e kon ko debbo on soktori. ∆äin ko keeri Alla, wata on jaggitu-…ói. kala jaggitu…óo keeri Alla …óin, ko …ďen ngoni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,230,"Si o seerii mo, on [debbo] dagitaŇčtaako mo …ďaawo …óu'um, haa o resindira e gorko goo. Si on [gorko] seerii mo, goopi fawaaki …ďe nde …ďe ruttondira, si …ďe fellitii √Īii…ďnugol keeri Alla …óin.∆äin ko keeri Allah, Himo ∆ĀaŇčnginana …ói …ďen yim…ďe nganndu…ďe"
  2,231,"Si on seerii rew…ďe …ďen, laje ma…ď…ďe …óen yottike: jogitoree-…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri maa accitoron …ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. Wata on jogitor …ďe lorrugol nde jaggitoton. Kala wa…óu…óo …óum, gom…óii o too√Īii hoore-makko. Wata on jogitor Aayeeje Alla …óen jalnori. Annditee neemaaji Alla …ói O Neemini e mo'on, e ko O Jippini e mo'on immorde e Deftere e √Ďee√Īal; Himo Wa'ajora …óum. Hulle Alla, nganndon pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  2,232,"Si on seerii rew…ďe …ďen, laje ma…ď…ďe …óen yottike, wata on laagu …ďe nde moodi…ď…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen resata …ďe; si …ďe welondirii hakkunde ma…ď…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. ∆äum no waajoree on taw…óo e mo'on no gom…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde. Ko jaŇčtana…óon koo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on, …ďuri laa…ďaande. Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,233,"Jibim…ďe …ďen yo muynin …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen duu…ďi …ói…ói timmu…ói; wonannde on faandii…óo timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaa…óo on, √Īammingol holitinira [rew…ďe] …ďen no mo∆ī∆īiri. WoŇčkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibin…óo on lorrire sabu …ďi…ó…óo makko on, wanaa jibinanaa…óo on kadi lorrirtee sabu …ďi…ó…óo makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru …óum. Si …ďe faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde ma…ď…ďe e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe. Si on faandike …óa…ď…ďude muyninanoowo on …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko …ďen [muyninoo…ďe] hanndi e mo∆ī∆īere.Hulee Alla, nganndon ko O Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"
  2,234,"∆Āen maayoo…ďe e mo'on …ďe acca suddii…ďe: yo …ďen habbiŇčtin ko'e ma…ď…ďe lebbi nayi e bal…óe sappo. Si …ďe yottike laje ma…ď…ďe …óen, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko …ďe wa…óani ko'e ma…ď…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. Alla Ko Humpitii…óo kon ko golloton"
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko wee…ďitoton, e sabboyde suddii…ďe …ďen, maa suu…óu…óon …óum ka woŇčkiiji mo'on. Alla No Anndi aray ka annditon fii ma…ď…ďe, ko woni tun, wata on fodondir e ma…ď…ďe [desal] e gunndoo: si wanaa nde wowloton koŇčngol mo∆ī∆īol, wata on fellitu humugol dewgal ngal haa lajal edda ngal yottoo. Ngande pellet Alla No Anndi ko woni e woŇčkiiji mo'on, ReŇčtee e Makko, nganndon pellet Alla Ko Haforoowo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddii…ďe …ďen ado on renndude e ma…ď…ďe maa jaŇčtanagol …ďe teŇče, dakmitee …ďe:no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol …ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri.Hannduyee fawii…óo mo∆īim…ďe …ďen"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddii…ďe …ďen ado on meemude …ďe, tawa on jaŇčtanike …ďe teŇče: ko feccere kon ko jaŇčti-…óon, si wanaa hara …ďe ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juu…óe mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afoto…óon …ďurata …ďa…ótinnde gom…óal. Wata on yejjitu …ďural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko Reenu…óo kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee e jul…óe …óen, e julde hakkundeere nden. Darano…óon Alla ko o to∆ī∆īinii…ďe"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppay…ďe maa wa…ó…óii…ďe. Si on hoolike, jaŇčtee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"∆Āen maayoo…ďe e mo'on …ďe acca suddii…ďe: ko wasiyanagol suddii…ďe …ďen dakmitor…óum haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiŇčgol …ďe. Si …ďe yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko …ďe wa…óani ko'e ma…ď…ďe e mo∆ī∆īere. Alla ko Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  2,241,"No woodani …ďen seeraa…ďe: dakamitorgol no mo∆ī∆īiri. ko goongofawii…óo gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀaŇčnginiraŇčta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, belajo'o on haqqilay"
  2,243,"E a tinaali …ďen njaltunoo…ďe e galleeji mu'un, kam…ďe ko …ďe guluuje, ka reenagol e maayde, Allaahu On Daalani …ďe: \"Maayee\", refti O Wuurniti …ďe? Pellet Alla ko Jom ∆Āural e dow yim…ďe …ďen, ko woni tun, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen njaanataa [Alla]"
  2,244,"Ha…ďee fii laawol Alla Ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on √Īawloowo Alla √Īamaande mo∆ī∆īere, O Sowitana mo nde cowalle …óuu…óu…óe? Alla No ∆Āi…óttina Himo Ya√Ī√Īa, ko faade ka Makko ruttete-…óon"
  2,246,"E a tinaali ngun mbatu …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'ila, …ďaawo Muusaa, tuma nde …ďe wi'annoo Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on: \"Imminan men lam…óo, men ha…ďa fii laawol Alla Ngol?\" O maaki: \"Hara on tijjaaki si hare nden farlaama e mo'on nde roŇčkoton ha…ďude?\" …ďe mbi'i: \"Ko ha…óata men ha…ďugol e fii laawol Alla Ngol, gom…óii men njaltinaama e galleeji amen e …ďi…ó…ďe amen?\" Nde hare nden farlanoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe hucciti, si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Alla Ko Anndu…óo too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,247,"Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on maakani …ďe:\"Alla Imminanii on Taaluuta laam…óo\". ∆Āe mbi'i:\"Hol no laamu laatoraŇčta mo e hoore amen,ko menen …ďuri mo haandude e laamu,o rokkaaka yaajeende jawdi?\" O maaki:\"Alla Su…ďike mo e dow mo'on,O ∆Āeydi mo yaajeende ka ganndal e ka …ďanndu\". Alla No Rokka Laamu Makko Ngun on Mo O Muuyi,Alla ko Yaaju…óo […ďural] Anndu…óo"
  2,248,"Annabaajo ma…ď…ďe on maakani …ďe: \"Nganndee Maande Alla nden, ko nde Arkawal ngal arata on; dee∆īere no e ndeer maggal, immorde ka Joomi mo'on, e ko heddinoo ko aalo Muusaa e aalo Haaruuna en acci, hara Malaa'ika en no ronndii ngal. Pellet no e koo ko jaŇčtaa …óoo, Maande wonannde on; si o laatike gom…óim…ďe"
  2,249,"Nde Taaluuta yaltidunoo e konu ngun, o maaki: \"Alla No Jarribora on caangol: kala yar…óo e maggol o jeyaaka e am, kala mo me…óaali ngol ko on …óon jeyaa e am, si wanaa on √Īe…óir…óo junngo mun √Īe…óannde\". ∆Āe yari e caangol ngol si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Nde o lummbunoo ngol, kaŇčko e …ďen gom…óim…ďe wondu…ďe e makko, …ďen mbi'i: \"Feere alanaa en e Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun\". ∆Āen fellitu…ďe hawray e Alla …ďen mbi'i: \"Heewii ka fedde tokosere fooliri fedde …óuu…óunde, duŇčayee Alla\". Pellet Alla No Wondi e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen"
  2,250,"Nde …ďe fee√Īannoo Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun, …ďe mbi'i: \"Joomi amen, Rufu mu√Īal e dow amen, TabiŇčtinaa teppe amen, Faabo-…óaa men e …ďee heefer…ďe"
  2,251,"∆Āe fooliri…ďe DuŇčayee Alla: Daawuuda wari Jaaluuta, Alla Rokki mo Laamu e Annabaaku, O Anndini mo kon ko O Muuyi. Si wanaano Ko Alla Du√Īirnoo yim…ďe …ďen yoga e dow yoga, leydi ndin bonayno. Kono Alla Ko Jom ∆Āural e dow winndere nden"
  2,252,"∆äen ko Aayeeje Alla, Me…óen JaŇčnga …óe e dow maa…óa wondude e Goonga, Pellet ko a jeyaa…óo e Nulaa…ďe …ďen"
  2,253,"∆Āen Nulaa…ďe, Men ∆Āurnii yoga ma…ď…ďe e dow yoga : No e ma…ď…ďe yeewtidu…ďe e Alla, O ∆ĀaŇčti darjaaji yoga e ma…ď…ďe; Men Rokki Iisaa, …ďi…ó…óo Maryama on, …ďanngannduyeeji Men semmbiniri mo fittaandu laa…ďundu ndun. Si Alla Muuyuno, wom…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďen wartindirtaano …ďaawo nde …ďanngannduyeeji …óin ari maab…ďe. Kono …ďe luutondiri: no e ma…ď…ďe …ďen gom…óim…ďe, no e ma…ď…ďe …ďen yeddu…ďe. Si Alla Muuyuno, …ďe wartindirtaano, kono Alla no wa…óa kon ko O Yi…ói"
  2,254,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, sakkee e kon ko Men Arsiki on adii √Īalaande arde; nde ngeyngu alaa e mayre, wanaa sehilaaku, wanaa tefoore. Ko heefer…ďe …ďen woni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,255,"Alla, alaa reweteezo si wanaa kanko, Wuur…óo √Ďii…ďu…óo. ŇäoŇčre nanngataa Mo, wanaa kadi …óoyngol. ko Kanko Jeyi huunde ko woni ka kammuuli e huunde ko woni ka leydi. Ko hommbo woni on tefoowo ka Makko si wanaa e duŇčayee Makko? Himo anndi ko woni yeeso ma…ď…ďe, e ko woni …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe hu…ďindotaako huunde e Anndal Makko ngal si wanaa ko O Muuyi. Jullere Makko nden no yaaji …ďuri kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Reenugol …ói aaninaa Mo. Ko Kano woni Toowu…óo Maw…óo On. @Corrected"
  2,256,"Doolugol alaa ka diina. Gom…óii peewal ngal …ďanngii immorde e majjere nden. Kala yeddu…óo …óuu…óa bewreeru ndun o gom…óini Alla, haray o jogitike …ďoggi finnde hoolaare …óin, firtagol alanaa …ói. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  2,257,"Alla Ko Gi…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen: Himo yaltina …ďe e ni…ďe, O na…ďa …ďe e ndaygu. ∆Āeya yeddu…ďe, yi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe ko …óuu…óa bewreeji …óin: Hi…ói yaltina …ďe e ndaygu na…ďa …ďe e ni…ďe. ∆Āen ko yim…ďe yiite, luttoo…ďe e magge"
  2,258,"E a yi'aali on wennju…óo Ibraahiima e fii Jey…óo mo On, fii Alla no Ye…ói mo laamu, nde Ibraahiima maakunoo: \"Jey…óo lam on, ko On Wuurnata Wara\". [Wennju…óo on] wi'i: \"Min kadi mi…óo wuurna wara\". Ibraahiima maaki: \"Pellet Alla no Addira naange ngen fu…ónaange, addir nge hiirnaange\".Yeddu…óo on mugaa. Alla fewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  2,259,"Wolla ko hono oon birtii…óo wuro yeewngo ngo maadi mum e mbildi mum yirbi o wi*i hono Alla wuurtaninta …óum caggal maayde mum? Alla wari mbo o lelii duu…ďi teemedere O ummini mbo O daali hono foti √Īii…ď…óa o wi*i √Īalawma maa feccere √Īalawma, O daali alah a duumiima …óo duu…ďi teemedere ∆īeew √Īaamdu ma e njaram ma waylaaki ndaaru mbabba ma ba, ngam min mba…ó ma maande wonande yim…ďe, ∆īeew ∆īi*e nomin cardata…óe refti Min muurda…óe teew, nde …óuum fee√Īi mbo o wi*i mi anndi Alla na hattani kala huunde…ď…ó∆ī∆ī√Īj"
  2,260,"Nde Ibraahiima maaki joom am hollam na nguurtanirta maay…ďe, O daali mate a goon…óinaani? o maaki ohonkay kono ko haa …ďernde am dee∆īa , O daali nanngu colli nay tappu…ói faade e ma refti mba…óa e kala tulde feccere e colli he refti noddu…ói …ói ngara e ma ho…ói njaha anndu Alla ko pooloowo mbo fooletaake ko O √Īee√Īo"
  2,261,Yeru …ďeen nafkoo…ďe e laawol Alla ko honbbere fu…ónunde butaali njee…ói…ói in wutaandu fof teemedere abbere Alla na sowana Mo O welaa Alla ko jaac…óo Ganndo
  2,262,Nafkoo…ďe jawdi mum en e laawol Alla refti …ďe ndewnatah e ko…ďe ko wacde wolla lor woodanii…ďe njobdi mum en ka joomi mum en kulol alanaa…ďe …ďe ngonah sunotoo…ďe
  2,263,"Konngol lobbol …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e sadaka dewnatee…óo lorla, Alla ko Gala yondanii…óo munyoowo"
  2,264,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe wotee mbonniree sadakuuji mon wacde e lorlude hono oon tottir…óo jawdi mum yeenga yim…ďe o goon…óinaani Alla e √Īalngu cakkatiingu o wayi kono haa∆īre …óaatnde to…ďo yani e mayre acci nde honde wa*i e teeleende …ďeen kattantah hay huunde e ko …ďe paggatii ko,Alla feewnatah yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďe"
  2,265,"Yeru …ďeen nafkoo…ďe jawdi mum en ngam …óa…ď…ďude welu Alla e tabatinde pittaali mum en ko hono ngesa ngonba e dow tulde to…ďo heewngo heewngo yani e heba ba, ba addi cowe …ói…ď…óe ko ba addatno si ba to…ďaam √Īuur √Īuur koba hecca mbelba balangol A na yi*a ko mba…óaton ko"
  2,266,"Mbela gooto e mon na yi…ói nde o da√Īata ngesa tamaro e inabeeje na ila e les mabba caatli te homba jogii e heba kala …ďeynaa…óe, o naywi hombo jogii …ďeyngu loongu henndu wondundu e yiite yana e ngesa he ba suma, ko hona nih Min …ďannganirta kaawisaaji …ói mbela miicta…óon"
  2,267,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe tottiree ko laa…ďi ummaade ko paggiti …óon e ko Min njaltinani on ka leydi, wotee paande ko so…ďi ko ngam nafkude heen on ngonah nanngoo…ďe …óum si wonah on meerni heen, ngannde Alla ko yondanii…óo Mantaa…óo"
  2,268,"Seytaane na fodana on baasal o yamira on pankare, Alla noon na fodana on yaafuya ummaade e Makko e …ďural Alla ko jaac…óo ko O Ganndo"
  2,269,"Hombo totta √Īee√Īal mbo O wela kala tottaa…óo √Īee√Īal o tottaa ma mo∆ī∆īere mawnde, siftortah …óum si wonah joman hakkiillaaji"
  2,270,"Kala ko tottir…óon e nafake wolla takku…óon e takkere pellet Alla na anndi …óuum, woodanaani too√Īoo…ďe walloo…ďe"
  2,271,Si on …ďannginii sadakeeji na ∆ī∆īi si on cuu…ói …ói tottu…óon …ói waas…ďe ko …óuum …ďuri on mo∆ī∆īande O hafrana on bon…ói mon Alla na humpitii ko golloton ko
  2,272,"A fawaaki peewal mum en kono ko Alla feewnata mbo O faala, kala ko tottir…óon e mo∆ī∆īere ko ko*e mon woodani on nafkatah si wonah ngam Alla kala ko tottir…óon e mo∆ī∆īere tottite …óum e mbaadi timmundi onon de on too√Īetaake"
  2,273,"Woodanii waas…ďe suraa…ďe gaa e laawol Alla …ďe mbaawah yaade e leydi hee, majju…ďe na cikka ko…ďe al…óu…ďe sabu …óuurnaade aduna ana anndira…ďe maandeeji mum en …ďe √Īaagataaka yim…ďe e mbaadi cattundi kala ko tottir…óon Alla na anndi …óum"
  2,274,"Tootiroo…ďe jawdi mum en jemma e √Īalawma e mbaadi mbirniindi e mbaadi …ďanngundi, …ďeen de woodanii…ďe njbdi mum en ummaade ka joomi mum en kulol woodanaani …ďe …ďe ngonah sunatoo…ďe"
  2,275,"…ďeen √Īaamoo…ďe riba …ďe ummataako si wonah no mbo seytaani memi …óuum noon ko sabu wiide …ďe pellet njeegu wa*i kono riba, Alla noon daknii njeeygu O harmini riba, kala mbo waaju ummmarii mbo ka Alla o acci woodanii mbo o …ďenni ko fiyaaku makko e Alla fawii, kala duttii…óo noon ko …ďeen ngoni joman en yiite saasoo…ďe e henge haa pooma"
  2,276,Alla na momto riba na …ďamta sadakuuji Alla yi…óah kala kee…óo keefeeru e bakkadinoowo sanne
  2,277,…ďeen goon…óin…ďe ngolli ko mo∆ī∆īi o darni juulde o tottiri askal woodanii…ďe jobdi mum en ummaade ko joomi mum en kulol alanaa…ďe …ďe ngonah sunatoo…ďe
  2,278,Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe kulee Alla accon ko heddii ko e riba si on ngonii goon…óu…ďe
  2,279,Si on mba…óaani …óuum kolliree hare ummorde e Alla e nelaa…óo MakkoJJJ…ďJ
  2,280,"Si tawii o wonii e satteende yo o mu√Īane haa e yaajeende,nde cakkorton …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e mon si on ngonii anndu…ďe"
  2,281,Kulee √Īalngu ngu nduttete…óon ka Alla refti yo…ďee kala fittaandu ko ndu faggitii ko kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake
  2,282,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe si on √Īamlandiri nyamaande faade happu dottaa…óo mbinndee nde, yo nuun…óu…óo winndu hakkunde mon, woto binndoowo sala winndude yo o winndu no Alla anndiniri mbo, yo o winndu yo mbo hakke woni dow mum winndu yo o hul joomiiko woto o ustu heen hay huunde, si wonii mbo hakke woni e dow mum ko …óaay…óo wolla loh…óo wollo o waawah fidde, yo keedo makko fidir nuun…óal, ceednee seede en …ói…óo e wor…ďe mon, si wor…ďe …ói…óo ngalah ko gorko e rew…ďe …ói…óo …ďe mbelete …óon e seedeeli ngam si gooto e ma…ď…ďe yrdditi go…ó…óo o siftirina mbo, woto seedeeli cala si…ďe noddaama, wote kaaste winndude ko fam…ói maa ko heewi faade e happu mum, ko …óuum …ďuri nuun…óude ka Alla …ďuri fooccaade wonande seede …ďuri kadi …ďadaade waasde mon sikkitaade, si wonah kommersaagu ngonaangu ngu yiilaton hakkunde mon, ndeen noon bakkaat alah e mon nde mbaasaton …óum winndude, ceetnee si on yeeyandiri woto binndoowo e seede lore, si on wa…óii …óuum pellet …óuum ko faasikaagal e mon, kulee Alla O anndina on Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,283,"Si on ngonii e …óatngal on ke…ďaani binndoowo tottirre jukunnde tamaande, si on koolandirii, oon tottaa…óo hoolaare yo tottit hoolaare nde, yo o hul Alla joom makko, wotee cuu…óe seedanfaagu kala cuu…óo ngu pellet oon …ďernde makko ko bakkadinnde, Alla na anndi ko ngollaton ko"
  2,284,"Woodanii Alla ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi si on …ďannginii ko e pittaali mon wolla on cuu…ói ma Alla haasbu mon sabu mum, O yaafoo mbo O wela O lepta mbo wela, Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde"
  2,285,"Nulaa…óo goon…óanii ko jippinaa ko e Makko ummade e Joom Makko, e goonin…ďe …ďe fof …ďe goon…óanii Alla e malaykaaji Makko e defte makko e Nulaa…ďe makko, min ceerndatah hay gooto e Nulaa…ďe makko, …ďe wii min nanii min …óoftiima hafran amen Joomi amen ko Mah woni ruttorde"
  2,286,"Alla fawatah fittaandu kondu hattanaani,woodanii ndu kondu faggii, fawiima e dow mayru kondu faggitii,Joomi amen woto nanngir min ko min njjiti ko wollo ko min ngoopi ko,woto A faw e amen tampere hono no ndoondirna…óa …ďeen adii…ďe amen,Joomi amen woto faw min komin kattanaani,yaafa amin cuura bakkatuuJi amen nJurma…óa min ko Aan woni keeda amin wollu min e dow yim…ďe heeferee…ďe …ďe"
  3,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  3,2,"Alla: rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko O Wuur…óo, √Ďii…ďu…óo"
  3,3,"O Jippinirii Deftere nden dow maa…óa e goonga, goonginnde ko adii nde, O Jippini Tawreeta e Linnjiila"
  3,4,"Ko adii, fii fewnugol yim…ďe …ďen, O Jippini AlQur'aana. Pellet yeddu…ďe Aayeeje Alla …óen, hino woodani …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe. Alla Ko Foolu…óo, Jom-yottagol"
  3,5,"Pellet, Alla, huunde suu…óotaako Mo ka leydi wanaa ka kammu"
  3,6,"Ko KaŇčko Woni Mbaadiniroowo on ka renngaaji noone woo no O Muuyiri. Rewetee…óo woo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko, Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,7,"Ko KaŇčko Woni Jippin…óo Deftere nden e maa…óa, no e mayre aayeeje …ďaŇčngu…óe; ko kaŇčje woni neene Deftere nden, e go…ó…óe goo nanndu…óe. Ammaa …ďen …ďe oo√Īaare woni e nder …ďer…óe mun, hi…ďe jokka ko nanndi kon e majje …óa…ď…ďugol fitina e …óa…ďugol firtugol …óe. Anndataa firo majje si wanaa Alla. Tutii…ďe …ďen e ganndal no wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii nde, kala mun ko immorde ka Joomi amen\". Waajitotaako si wanaa joomiraa…ďe haqqillaaji …ďen"
  3,8,"joomi amen, wata oo√Īu …ďer…óe amen …óen …ďaawo nde fewnu-…óaa men, ye…óu men yurmeende immorde ka Maa…óa.Pellet An, ko An Woni Ye…óoowo=dokko"
  3,9,"Joomi amen, pellet An ko A Moo…ďoyoowo yim…ďe …ďen √Īalnde nde sikke alah e mun Pellet Alla luutintaa fodoore nden"
  3,10,"Pellet …ďen yeddu…ďe, jawle ma…ď…ďe e …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe duncaŇčtaa…ďe e lepte Alla …óen hay e huunde. Ko …ďen woni carmale yiite ngen"
  3,11,"Wano mbowdi yim…ďe Fir'awna e …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe. ∆Āe fennii aayeeje Amen …óen, Alla Nanngitiri …ďe junubaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Alla ko Sa…ótu…óo lepte"
  3,12,"Maakan …ďen yeddu…ďe: \"On fooloyte moo…ďoye-…óon ka jahannama\". Nge bonii nda…ó…óudi"
  3,13,"Gom…óii laatanike on aaya e …óin feddeejji …ói…ói fottu…ói fiiha…ďugol: fedde goo no ha…ďa e laawol Alla, wonnde goo ko yeddunde, hi…ďe yi'ira…ďe yeru ma…ď…ďe laaw…ďi …ói…ói gii…óe gite. Alla no Semmbinira balla Makko ngal o Mo O Muuyi. Pellet, no e …óum waaju wonannde joomiraa…ďe-haqqillaaji"
  3,14,"Yim…ďe …ďen cu…óinanaama yi…óugol tuuyooji: immorde e rew…ďe e …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe, e jawle tuginidiraa…óe, immorde e kaŇčŇče e kaalise, e pucci Ňčar…ói…óaa…ói, e neemoraa…ói, e remuru. ∆äum …óon, ko dakamme nguurdam aduna. Alla, no ka Makko mo∆ī∆īu…óum ruttorde"
  3,15,"Maaku: \"E yo mi humpitu on ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e …óum mon?\". No woodani …ďen hulu…ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, aljannaaji, no ila senngo ley majji, can…ói: ko …ďe luttoo…ďe ton, wondude e sonnaa…ďe la…ď…ďinaa…ďe, e yerluyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko ReŇčtu…óo jeyaa…ďe …ďen. @Corrected"
  3,16,"∆Āen wi'oo…ďe: \"Joomi amen, menen men gom…óinii, yawtan men junubaaji amen, da…óndaa men lepte yiite"
  3,17,Mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen e goongu…ďe …ďen e …óoftii…ďe …ďen e wiŇčtoo…ďe=nafkoobe …ďen e insinotoo…ďe …ďen ka hoore-subaka
  3,18,"Alla Seedike wonde Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa kaŇčko, Malaa'ika en kadi, e joomiraa…ďe ganndal …ďen, ko O Daranii…óo nun…óal. Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko, On Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,19,"Pellet diina kan ka Alla, ko lislaamu. Okkaa…ďe Defte …ďen lurraali si wanaa …ďaawo nde ganndal ngal arde …ďe; ka bewre hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Kala yeddu…óo aayeeje Alla …óen, pellet Alla ko yaawu…óo hasboore"
  3,20,"Si …ďe wennjii ma, maaku: \"Mi jebbilanii yeeso an ngon e on jokku…óo lam\". Maakanaa …ďen okkaa…ďe Defte e humambinne en: \" E on jebbilike?\" Si …ďe jebbilike, gom…óii …ďe feewii, si …ďe huccitii, enee, ko fawi maa ko yottingol. Alla ko ReŇčtu…óo jeyaa…ďe …ďen"
  3,21,"Pellet, …ďen yeddoo…ďe aayeeje Alla …óen, …ďe wara Annabaa…ďe …ďen ko aldaa e goonga, …ďe wara …ďen yamiroo…ďe nun…óal, wewlinir …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  3,22,"Ko …ďen woni …ďe golleeji mun boni …ďen ka aduna e ka laakara, …ďe alaa walloo…ďe"
  3,23,"E a yi'aali okkaa…ďe ge…ďal e Deftere nden, hi…ďe noddee e Deftere Alla nden fii no nde √Īaawira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, refti fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe huccita ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe"
  3,24,"∆äum non, ko tawde …ďe wi'ii: \"Yiite ngen meemataa men si wanaa √Īal…ói limtaa…ói\". hodii…ďe e diina ma…ď…ďe kan, huunde nde …ďe fefindotonoo"
  3,25,"E ko hol no si Men Moo…ďoyii…ďe e √Ďalaande nde sikke alaa e mu'un, woŇčkii kala hunnanee ko ki faggitii kon? Kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake"
  3,26,"Maaku: \"Yaa An Laam…óo Jey…óo laamu, Hi…óa Okka laamu on mo Muuyu…óaa, Hi…óa ∆Āoora laamu on mo Muuyu…óaa, Hi…óa Teddina on mo Muuyu…óaa, Hi…óa Hoyna on mo Muuyu…óaa. Mo∆ī∆īere nden ko e Junngo Maa…óa woni, pellet, An e huunde kala, ko A Haa…ótan…óo"
  3,27,"Hi…óa Naadira jemma on nder √Īalorma on, Hi…óa Naadira √Īalorma on nder jemma on. Hi…óa Yaltina ko wuuri immorde e ko maayi, yaltinaa ko maayi immorde e ko wuur. Hi…óa Arsika on mo Muuyu…óaa ko aldaa e hasboore"
  3,28,"Wata muumini en jogitor heefer…ďe …ďen yi…ó…ďe …ďe acca gom…óim…ďe …ďen. Kala huuwu…óo …óum, o laataaki jeyraa…óo e diina Alla Kan hay e huunde, si wanaa nde huloton e ma…ď…ďe bone. Alla No ReŇčtina on Hoore-Mun. Ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  3,29,"Maaku:Si on suu…óii ko woni e …ďer…óe mon maa si on fe√Ī√Īin …óum,Alla no Anndi …óum,Himo Anndi ko woni ka kammuuli e ko woni e leydi Alla ko kattan-…óo kala huunde"
  3,30,"√Ďalnde kala woŇčkii tawata ko ki golli kon e mo∆ī∆īere hino …ďannaa, e huunde ko ki golle e bone, ki yeloo sinno wonayno hakkunde makki e majje dumunne wo…ó…óu…óo. Alla no ReŇčtina on Hoore Mun. Alla ko Hilnotoo…óo jeyaa…ďe …ďen"
  3,31,"wi*u si wonii hidon yidi Alla, cukke e am, mi yidno mon Alla, O yaafo mon bakkatuuji mon, Alla ko kafroowo jumotoodo"
  3,32,"Maaku: \"∆äoftee Alla e Nulaa…óo on\", si …ďe huccitii, pellet, Alla yi…óaa yeddu…ďe …ďen"
  3,33,"Pellet, Alla Su…ďike Aadama e Nuuhu e yim…ďe Ibraahiima …ďen e yim…ďe Imraana …ďen e hoore tagoore nden"
  3,34,Jurriiya=genyol yoga e ma…ď…ďe iwde e yoga. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo
  3,35,"Nde debbo Imraana on wi'unoo: \"Joomi an, min mi takkanii Ma kon woni ka nder reedu am, ko rin…óinaa …óum, ja…ďanam, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  3,36,"Nde o jibinnoo mo o wi'i: \"Min mi jibinii mo ko o deyel\", ko Alla …ďuri Anndude ko O jibini, gorko laataaki wano debbo. \"Min mi innii mo Maryama, min mi moolnii mo e Maa…óa e jurriiya makko on immorde seytaane ra…óaa…óo on"
  3,37,"Joomi makko Ja…ďirani mo ja…ďannde mo∆ī∆īere,O Neiri mo needi mo∆ī∆īundi,O Halfini mo Jakariya.Tuma kala Jakariya naati e hoore makko ka Mihraab,o tawda mo e arsike,o wi'a:Hey, Mariyam hol no he…ďir…óaa …óum?O jaaboo:∆äum ko ka Alla iwri.Pellet,no Arsika on O Muuyi ko aldaa e hasboore"
  3,38,"Ko ton Jakariraa'u noddi Jooma mun o maaki: \"Joomi am, Ye…óam immorde ka Maa…óa, jurriiya laa…ďu…óo, pellet, An ko A Nanoowo noddaandu"
  3,39,"Malaa'ika en noddi mo hawri himo darii juuugol ka ganngunal, wonde: \"Alla No Wewlinire Yahyaa, goongin…óo Konngol iwrungol ka Alla: koohoojo, e reenaa…óo [e tuuyo], e Annabaajo jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe\" @Corrected"
  3,40,"O maaki: \"Joomi an, hol no …ďi…ó…óo laatorŇčta lam, gom…óii mi nawyii, debbo am on ko damaro?\" O Daali: \"Ko wano non Alla Wa…óirta ko O Muuyi [wa…óde]"
  3,41,"O maaki: \"Joomi, Wa…óanam maande\". O Daali: \"Maande maa nden, ko nde a yeewtidataa e yim…ďe …ďen …ďal…óe tati si wanaa e joopagol. JaŇčto…óaa Joomi maa…óa ko heewi: subbunhino-…óaa kiiki e bimmbi"
  3,42,"Tuma nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, pellet Alla Su…ďike ma, O La…ď…ďinii ma [O Su…ďii] e rew…ďe winndere nden"
  3,43,"Hey Maryam, to∆ī∆īinano Joomi maa, sujjaa ru∆ī∆īidaa e ru∆ī∆īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,44,"∆äum …óoo, ko jeyaa…óum e kumpite wirnii…óe, Me…óen Wahayina …óe e maa…óa. A tawanooka e ma…ď…ďe nde …ďe weddotonoo ku…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin: ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe ne'ata Maryama; a tawanooka e ma…ď…ďe kadi nde …ďe wennjaynoo"
  3,45,"Nde Malaa'ika en wi'unoo: \"Hey Maryama, Alla no Wewlinire Konngol immorde e Maako: Innde makko, ko meema-sella, Iisaa ge…óal Maryama, koohoojo aduna e laakara, jeyaa…óa e …ďa…ótinaa…ďe [ka Alla]"
  3,46,"Himo yeewtida e yim…ďe …ďen ka woofordu=tiggu e ka sagatalaaku, ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen"
  3,47,"O wi'i: \"Joomi am, hol no …ďi…ó…óo laatoraŇčta lam, …ďanndiŇčke meemaali lam?\". O Daali: \"Ko wano non. Alla no Taga ko O Muuyi. Si O √Ďaawii fiyaake, O Daalanay mo [tun]: \"Laato! o laatoo"
  3,48,Himo Anndina mo Deftere nden e √Ďee√Īal ngal e Tawreeta e Linnjiila
  3,49,"E Nulaa…óo faade e …ďi…ď…ďe Israa'iila en, wonnde: \"Gom…óii mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Wonnde mi…óo tagana on immorde e loopal ko wa'i wa sonndu, mi wutta e muu…óum woŇčtira sonndu e DuŇčayee Alla. Mi wumtina bun…óo, mi sellina baadaa…óo, mi wuurnitira maay…ďe e duŇčayee Alla. Mi humpita on ko √Īaamoton e ko maroton ka cuu…ói mon. Pellet, hino e …óum, maande wonanannde on si on laatike gom…óim…ďe"
  3,50,"e goongin…óo ko woni yeeso am immorde e Tawreeta, e no mi dagininirana on yoga e ko harmannoo on, mi addanii on maande immorde ka Joomi mon. Hulee Alla …óofto…óon lam"
  3,51,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon, rewee Mo. Ko …óum woni laawol focciingol"
  3,52,"Tuma nde Iisaa so'unoo keeferaaku ngun e ma…ď…ďe, o maaki: \"Ko hommbo wallata lam e [diina] Alla [kan]?\". HawaaruyaŇčko en wi'i: \"Menen ko men walloo…ďe [e diina] Alla [kan], men gom…óinii Alla, seedo wonnde ko men jebbiilii…ďe"
  3,53,"Joomi amen, men gom…óinii ko Jipin…óaa Kon, men jokkii Nulaa…óo on, Winndu men e seedii…ďe …ďen"
  3,54,∆Āe fewji Alla Kadi Fewji. Ko Alla ∆Āuri Mo∆ī∆īude e fewjoo…ďe …ďen
  3,55,"Nde Alla Daalunoo: \"Hey Iisaa, Min ko mi Hunnoowo ma e ∆Āamtoowo ma faade ka Am, e La…ď…ďinoowo ma immorde e …ďen yeddu…ďe, e Wa…óa …ďen jokku…ďe ma e hoore …ďen yeddu…ďe haa √Ďalnde Darngal. Refti ko faade ka Am woni ruttorde mon, Mi √Ďaawa hakkunde mon ko luutondirayno-…óon e muu…óum"
  3,56,"Ammaa …ďen yeddu…ďe, Mi Lepta …ďen …óon lepte muusu…óe ka aduna e ka laakara, alanaa…ďe faabotoo…ďe"
  3,57,"Ammaa …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle-mo∆ī∆īe, O Hunnanay …ďe mbarjaari ma…ď…ďe ndin. Alla Yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,58,"∆äum …óoo, Me…óen Janngana maa …óum, immorde e Aayeeje e JaŇčtoore √Ďe√Ī√Īaannde"
  3,59,"Pellet, sifa Iisaa ka Alla, ko sifa Aadama; O Tagii mo immorde e mbummbuldi, refti O Daalani mo: \"Laato!\" o laatii"
  3,60,"Goonga kan ko ko immori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e …ďen sikkitii…ďe"
  3,61,"Kala wennju…óo ma fii makko …ďaawo kon ko ar e maa e ganndal, maaku: \"Aree nodden …ďi…ó…ďe amen e …ďi…ó…ďe mo'on, e rew…ďe amen e rew…ďe mo'on, e ko'e amen e ko'e mo'on, refti √Īaago…óen wa…óen kuddi Alla ndin e hoore fenoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,62,"Pellet …óum …óoo, ko …óum woni fillayee goonga. Alaa rewetee…óo si wanaa Alla, pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko Woni Foolu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,63,"Si …ďe huccitii, pellet Alla ko Anndu…óo bonnoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,64,"Maaku: \"Hey yim…ďe Defte, aree faade e konngol fotayngol hakkunde amen e mo'on : wonnde en rewataa si wanaa Alla, en kafidataa Mo e huunde, wata yoga e me'en jogito yoga joomiraa…ďe ko woori Alla\". Si …ďe huccitii, wi'ee: \"Seeditee wonnde menen ko men jebbilii…ďe"
  3,65,"Hey yim…ďe Defte, ko wennjaŇčton fii Ibraahiima, Tawreeta e Linnjiila Jippinaaka si wanaa …ďaawo makko : e on haqqiltaa"
  3,66,"Hey ko onon …ďee, on wennjii kon ko anndal woodani on e mu'un, ko wennjaŇčton ko anndal alanaa on e mu'un? Alla no Anndi onon on anndaa"
  3,67,"Ibraahiima laatanooki AlyahuudiŇčke wanaa Annasaaraajo, si ko woni, o laatinoke oo√Īii…óo [e kala diina] jebbilanii…óo [Diina Lislaamu], o laatanooki jeyaa…óo e shirkoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,68,"Pellet, ko …ďuri hanndude e Ibraahiima e yim…ďe …ďen : ko …ďen jokku…ďe mo, e oo Annabiijo, e …ďen gom…óim…ďe. Alla ko Gi…óo gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  3,69,"Fedde goo e yim…ďe Defte …ďen yelike nde …ďe majjina on, …ďe majjiŇčtaa si wanaa ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe so'aa anndude"
  3,70,"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko yeddaŇčton Aayeeje Alla ∆äen hara onon ko on seedii…ďe"
  3,71,"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko jillaŇčton goonga kan e meh-re nden hi…óon suu…óa goonga kan hara onon hi…óon anndi"
  3,72,"Fedde goo jeyaande e yim…ďe Defte …ďen wi'i: \"Gom…óinee ko jippinaa kon e …ďen gom…óim…ďe ka arannde √Īallal, yeddon ka sakkitoode mayre, bela jo'o, …ďe ruttoo"
  3,73,"Wata on gom…óin si wanaa on jokku…óo diina mon kan\". Maaku: \"Pellet, ko Peewal Alla ngal woni Peewal\". [Ko kulil fii ] wata go…ó…óo goo okke sugu ko okka…óon kon maa …ďe wennjiroya on …óum ko Joomi mon. Maaku: \"Pellet …ďural ngal ko e Junngo Alla woni, Himo Ye…óa ngal on Mo O Muuyi\". Alla ko yaaju…óo […ďural] Anndu…óo"
  3,74,Himo Hertinana Yurmeende Makko nden on Mo O muuyi. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural Mawngal
  3,75,"No e yim…ďe Defte …ďen, on mo halfiŇčtaa jawdi wonayndi KINTAAR, on jonnite ndi; hino e ma…ď…ďe kadi, on mo halfiŇčtaa \"diinaaru\", on jonnitataa ma ndu si wanaa a darani mo daŇčkaranni-…óaa. ∆äum non, ko tawde kam…ďe …ďe wi'i: \"Laatanaaki men e humammbinnee…ďe …ďen laawol\"; hi…ďe ta∆īa penaale huma e Alla hara kam…ďe hi…ďe anndi"
  3,76,"Aa'a, kala hunnu…óo ahadi mu'un o huli, pellet, Alla no Yi…ói huloo…ďe Mo …ďen"
  3,77,"∆Āen soktitoray…ďe ahadi Alla ndin e goondooje ma…ď…ďe coggeloy fam…óukoy, …ďen …óon, ge…ďal alaa …ďe ka laakara, Alla yeewtidataa e ma…ď…ďe, O Ndaaroytaa …ďe √Ďlande Darngal, O La…ď…ďiŇčtaa …ďe, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  3,78,"No e ma…ď…ďe fedde : hi…ďe oo√Īira …óem…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e Deftere nden no sikkiron …óum ko jeyaa…óum e Deftere nden, …óum le jeyaaka e Deftere nden; hi…ďe wi'a : \"∆äum ko ko iwri ka Alla\", …óum le wanaa ka Alla iwri; hi…ďe takka penaale hoore Alla hara kam…ďe hi…ďe anndi"
  3,79,"Laatanaaki …ďanndiŇčke nde Alla Okkata mo Deftere e fahmu e Annabaaku, refti o wi'ana yim…ďe …ďen: \"Laatee jeyaa…ďe am ko woori Alla\", si ko woni: \"Laatoree tutii…ďe-e-gannde-diina, ko laatino…óon hi…óon janngina Deftere nden e ko laati…óon hi…óon jannga\" @Corrected"
  3,80,Wanaa nde o yamirta on jogitorgol Malaa'ika en e Annabaa…ďe …ďen rewetee…ďe. E o yamiray on keeferaaku …ďaawo nde won…óon jul…ďe
  3,81,"Tuma nde Alla ∆īettunoo ahadi e Annabaa…ďe …ďen : \"Si Mi Addanii on Deftere e fahmu, refti Nulaa…óo ari e mo'on goongin…óo kon ko jogi…óon, ma on gom…óin mo wallito…óon mo\". O Daali: \"E on qirritike …óum, on ∆īettii e hoore mun ahadi?\". ∆Āe wi'i: \"Men qirritike\". O Daali: \"Seeditee, Mi…óo wondi e mo'on ka seeditii…ďe"
  3,82,"On huccitu…óo …ďaawo …óum, ko …ďen woni faasiqii…ďe …ďen"
  3,83,"E ko woori Diina Alla kan …ďe …óa…ď…ďata? Hino woodani Mo jebbilaare …ďen won…ďe ka kammuuli e ka leydi, …óoftaare maa waawneede, ko faade ka Makko …ďe ruttotoo"
  3,84,"Maaku: \"Men gom…óinii Alla e ko jippinaa dow amen e ko jippinaa dow Ibrahiima e Isma'iila e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba e Taaniraa…ďe …ďen e ko Muusaa e Iisaa okkaa e Annabaa…ďe …ďen immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e ma…ď…ďe, Menen wonannde Mo ko men jebbilii…ďe"
  3,85,"Kala …óa…ď…ďu…óo ko woori Lislaamu on Diina, o ja…ďaŇčtaake …óum, on …óon ka laakara, ko o jeyaa…óo e hayru…ďe …ďen"
  3,86,"Hol no Alla Fewnirta yim…ďe yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe …ďe seedii wonnde Nulaa…óo on ko goonga, …ďanngannduyeeji …óin arii …ďe? Alla Fewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,87,"∆Āen …óon, jo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, ko no fawii …ďe kuddi Alla ndin e Malaa'ika en e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe denndaangal"
  3,88,"Ko …ďe luttoo…ďe e magge. ∆Āe hayfinaŇčtaake lepte …óen, …ďe wonaali nennanaŇčtee…ďe"
  3,89,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko Yaafotoo…óo Yurmetee…óo"
  3,90,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe, refti …ďe …ďeydorii keeferaaku, tuubugol ma…ď…ďe ja…ďetaake; ko …ďen …óon woni majju…ďe …ďen"
  3,91,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe maayi ko …ďe heerer…ďe, gooto e ma…ď…ďe ja…ďaŇčtaake, leydi ndin tew kaŇčŇče; hay si o soktorii …óum. ∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe, …ďe alaa walloo…ďe"
  3,92,"On he…ďataa mo∆ī∆īere nden haa wiŇčto…óon e ko …ďuru…óon yi…óude kon. Kala woo ko wiŇčti…óon, pellet Alla no Anndi …óum"
  3,93,"Kala √Īaametee laatino daganii-…óum …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila en, si wanaa ko Israa'iila harminanno hoore-mun ado Tawreeta Jippaade. Maaku: \"Addee Tawreetaare nden janngon nde, si on laatiima goongu…ďe"
  3,94,"Kala fefindii…óo fenaande [dammbi] e Alla …ďaawo …óum, ko …ďen …óon woni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,95,"Maaku: \"Alla goongii. Jokke diina Ibraahiima kan; oo√Īiika [gaa diinaaji mehre], o laatanooki jeyaa…óo e …ďen sirkoo…ďe"
  3,96,"Pellet, aranndu e Suudu wa…óanaandu yim…ďe …ďen, ko ndun wondu Bakkata; barkinaandu e peewal wonannde Winndere nden"
  3,97,"Ino e mayru Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe : darorde Ibraahiima nden. Kala naatu…óo e mayru, o laatoo hoolii…óo. No woodani Alla e dow yim…ďe …ďen hajjugol ka Suudu [hormaandu], wonannde on hattan…óo e mayru laawol. Kala on yeddu…óo, pellet, Alla ko Yonndinii…óo e winndere nden"
  3,98,"Maaku: \"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, e ko yeddanton Aayeeje Alla …óen, Alla ko Seedii…óo ko golloton kon"
  3,99,"Maaku: \"Hey mon yim…ďe Defte, ko faloto…óon e laawol Alla ngol, on gom…óin…óo Hi…óon …óa…ď…ďana ngol oo√Īan…óe hara ko on seedii…ďe! Alla wonaali Welsindii…óo e ko golloton kon"
  3,100,"Hey mon gom…óim…ďe, si on …óoftike fedde e …ďen okkaa…ďe Defte, …ďe ruttay on heefer…ďe …ďaawo gom…óinal mon"
  3,101,"E ko honno yeddirton nde tawnoo Aayeeje Alla …óen no janngeede e dow moo…óon, Nulaa…óo Makko on kadi no hakkunde mo'on? Kala on moolii…óo e Alla, gom…óii o fewnaama e laawol foccii ngol"
  3,102,"Hey mon gom…óim…ďe, huliree Alla no O Haaniri hulireede, wata on maayu dey, si wanaa hara ko on jebbilii…ďe"
  3,103,"Jogitee …ďoggol Alla ngol on denndaangal, wata on sertu. JaŇčto…óon Neema Alla on e dow moo…óon nde laatino…óon ayru…ďe, O Woowindiri hakkunde …ďer…óe mon …óen woŇčtir…óon Neema Makko on si…ó…óu…ďe; on laatioke e tonndu ngayka yiite, O Da…óndi on e magge. ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀannginiraŇčta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, bela jo'o, on feeway"
  3,104,"Yo laato e moo…óon mofte : noddooje e mo∆ī∆īere, yamiroo…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi ha…óoo…ďe ko a√Īinii. Ko …ďen …óon woni malaa…ďe …ďen"
  3,105,"Wata on laato wa …ďen sertu…ďe lurri …ďaawo nde …ďanngannduyeeji …óin ari e ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āen …óon, no woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  3,106,"√Ďalnde geece rawnata geece goo …ďawla. Si ko …ďen …ďe geece mu'un …ďawli : \"e on yeddu …ďaawo gom…óinal mon? Mee…óiree lepte …óen sabu ko laatino…óon hi…óon yedda"
  3,107,"Si ko …ďen …ďe geece mun rawni, …ďe wonii e nder Yurmeende Alla, kam…ďe ko …ďe luttoo…ďe ton"
  3,108,"∆äee …óoo, ko Aayeeje Alla, Me…óen Janngira …óe e dow maa…óa e goonga. Alla wonaali muuyoowo too√Īe e e winndere he"
  3,109,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, ko faade ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  3,110,"On laatike mofte …ďur…óe mo∆ī∆īude yaltinanaa…óe yim…ďe …ďen:hi…óon yamiraa ko mo∆ī∆īi ha…óon ko a√Īinii,hi…óon gom…óini Alla.Si yim…ďe Defte …ďen gom…óinno,…óum laatotono mo∆ī∆īere wonannde …ďe.No e ma…ď…ďe gom…óim…ďe, kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude ko e ma…ď…ďe ko faasiqeebe"
  3,111,"∆Āe lorrirtaa on si wanaa lorra […óem…óe]. Si …ďe ha…ďii on, …ďe hucciŇčtinany on …ďabbe, hooti …ďe walletaake"
  3,112,"Koyeera faŇčtike …ďe nokku kala ka …ďe tawaa, si wanaa …ďe ∆īettu ahadi ka Alla e ka yim…ďe …ďen. ∆Āe hootidi e tikkere immorde ka Alla …ďe huu…ďiŇčtiniraa baasal : …óum non, ko tawde …ďe laatinoke hi…ďe yedda Aayeeje Alla …óen, …ďe wara Annabaa…ďe …ďen ko aldaa e goonga. ∆äum non, ko sabu ko …ďe yeddi kon, …ďe laatii jaggitoo…ďe"
  3,113,"∆Āe wonaali fotay…ďe. No e yim…ďe Defte …ďen fedde feewunde : hi…ďe jannga Aayeeje Alla …óen saangaaji jemma, hi…ďe sujja"
  3,114,"Hi…ďe gom…óina Alla e √Ďalannde Sakkitiinde nden, hi…ďe yamira ko mo∆ī∆īi ha…óa ko a√Īinii, hi…ďe yaccoo e mo∆ī∆īereeje. ∆Āen ko jeyaa…ďe e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen"
  3,115,"Huunde woo ko …ďe huuwi e mo∆ī∆īere, …ďe yeddantaake …óum. Alla ko Anndu…óo huloo…ďe …ďen"
  3,116,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe, jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen dunncantaa- …ďe …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen e lepte Alla …óen hay huunde. Ko …ďen …óon woni yim…ďe yiite …ďen : kam…ďe ko …ďe luttoo…ďe ton"
  3,117,"Sifa ko …ďe nafqata kon e …óam nguurndam aduna; no wa'i wa henndu, no e mayru …ďuu…ďol, ndu hawri e co√Īal yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe, ndu halka mba[ngesa]. Alla Too√Īaali …ďe, si ko woni, ko ko'e ma…ď…ďe …ďe too√Īi"
  3,118,"Hey mon yo gom…óim…ďe, wata on jogito weldii…ďe ko woori on : …ďe ra…ď…ďindinaŇčtaako on e fii bonnugol on. ∆Āe yelike nde tampoton. Gom…óii ngayngu ngun fee√Īirii ka kunndule ma…ď…ďe, ko ko …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen suu…ói kon …ďuri mawnude.Gom…óii Men ∆Āannginanii on Aayeeje …óen, si on laatike haqqiloo…ďe"
  3,119,"Onon …ďee, hi…óon yi…ói …ďe kam…ďe …ďe yi…óaa on. Hi…óon gom…óini Deftere nden fow, si …ďe hawrii e mo'on, …ďe wi'a: \"Men gom…óinii\", si …ďe weddike, …ďe Ňčatana on kolli immorde e tikkere. Maaku: \"Maayee e tikkere mon\", pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo ko woni e …ďer…óe"
  3,120,"Si mo∆ī∆īere he…ďii on, metta …ďe, si bone kadi he…ďii on, …ďe weltora …óum. Si on mu√Ī√Īike on gom…óii, pewje ma…ď…ďe …óen lorrataa on hay huunde. Pellet, Alla ko Huu…ďitii…óo golle ma…ď…ďe"
  3,121,"Tuma nde dawno…óaa ka …ďeynguure maa…óa, hi…óa werna muumini en tommbor…óe hare. Alla ko Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  3,122,"Tuma nde feddeeji …ói…ói e mo'on himmu no, nde cooyoton, ko Alla non woni Gi…óo ma…ď…ďe. Ko Alla woni ko gom…óim…ďe …ďen haani hoolorde"
  3,123,"Gom…óii Alla Wallii on √Īalnde Badri, tawi ko on hoy…ďe. Hulee Alla, belajo'o on yettay [Mo]"
  3,124,"Nde maakanayno…óaa gom…óim…ďe …ďen: \"Enee, yonaŇčtaa on nde Joomi mo'on …ďeydanta on Malaa'ikaa…ďe guluuje tato jippinaa…ďe"
  3,125,"Pellet, si on mu√Ī√Īike on gom…óii, e arday on hawjere ma…ď…ďe, …óum …óoo, Joomi mo'on no ∆Āeydira on guluuje jowi Malaa'ika maandinaa…ďe"
  3,126,"Alla Wa…óiraali …óum si wanaa wewlere wonannde on, e no …ďer…óe mon …óen …óee∆īira …óum. Ballal iwrataa si wanaa ka Alla, On Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  3,127,"Ko fii yo O Ta∆īu fedde e …ďen yeddu…ďe maa O Wirta …ďe, …ďe ruttoo ko …ďe sooyu…ďe"
  3,128,"Laatanaaki ma e fiyaake on hay e huunde : maa O Ja…ďan …ďe tuubuubuyee, maa O Leptu …ďe, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe too√Īoo…ďe"
  3,129,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo Haforana on mo O Muuyi, O Lepta on mo O Muuyi. Alla ko Haforoowo Yurmetee…óo"
  3,130,"Hey mon yo gom…óim…ďe, wata on √Īaamu ribaa, cowalle sowaa…óe. Hulee Alla, belajo'o, on malete"
  3,131,Hulee ngen yiite maranaange …ďen heefer…ďe
  3,132,"∆äoftee Alla e Nulaa…óo on, belajo'o, on yurmete"
  3,133,"Yaccee faade e haforanal immorde ka Joomi mo'on e Aljanna, yannji Makko ndin no fota [e yaajeendi] kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, o maranaama …ďen gom…óu…ďe"
  3,134,"∆Āen nafqoo…ďe ka neweende e ka sa…óteende neweende, e …ďen suu…óoo…ďe tikkere, e …ďen yaafotoo…ďe yim…ďe …ďen. Alla no Yi…ói mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,135,"e …ďen taw…ďe si …ďe huuwii panŇčkare maa …ďe too√Īii ko'e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe anndita Alla …ďe insinanoo junuubi ma…ď…ďe …óin. E ko hommbo haforata si wanaa Alla? Hara …ďe deppitaaki e ko …ďe huuwi kon, tawa hi…ďe anndi"
  3,136,"∆Āen …óon, njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin ko yaafuyee immorde ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, e Aljannaaji : no ila e ley majji, can…ói, duumotoo…ďe ton. Mo∆ī∆īii mbarjaari golloo…ďe …ďen. @Corrected"
  3,137,Gom…óii yawtii ado mon …óate. Yahee ka leydi ndaaron hol no battane fennunoo…ďe …ďen laatornoo
  3,138,"∆äum …óoo, ko ∆Āanngannduyee wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, e peewal e waaju wonannde gom…óu…ďe …ďen"
  3,139,"Wata on lo'ino, wata on suno, ko onon woni toowu…ďe …ďen, si on laatike gom…óim…ďe"
  3,140,"Si barme he…ďii on, gom…óii barme sugu mun he…ďii yim…ďe …ďen. ∆äii √Īal…ói, Me…óen Yiltindira …ói hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen, e fii no Alla Anndira gom…óim…ďe …ďen, O Jogitoo e moo…óon seedatoo…ďe. Alla Yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,141,e fii yo Alla La…ď…ďin …ďen gom…óim…ďe O Halka heefer…ďe …ďen
  3,142,Kaa on sikku on naatay Aljanna hara Alla Anndaali …ďen ti…ónii…ďe e moo…óon O Annda mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen
  3,143,"Gom…óii on laatike hi…óon yeloo maayde nden ado on hawrude e mayre, gom…óii on yi'ii nde hi…óon ndaara"
  3,144,"Muhammadu wonaali si wanaa Nulaa…óo : gom…óii fe∆ī∆īii ko adii mo Nulaa…ďe. E si o faatike maa o waraama, on waylitoto e ba…óte [keeferaaku] mo'on ? Kala waylitii…óo e ba…óte mu'un, o lorrirtaa Alla hay e huunde, arma Alla Yo…ďita …ďen jaarnoo…ďe [Mo]"
  3,145,"Laatanaaki wonki nde ki maayata si wanaa e duŇčayee Alla. Ko winndaa…óum [wa…óanaa] lajal. Mo faandike njo…ďdi aduna, Men Okkay mo e mayri, mo faandike kadi njo…ďdi laakara, Men Okkay mo e mayri, arma Men Yo…ďa jaarnoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,146,"Heewii e Annabaa…ďe …ďe ha…ďi wondude e ma…ď…ďe jamaaji …óuu…óu…ói, …ďe lo'inanooki sabu ko he…ďi …ďe kon e laawol Alla, …ďe lo'aano …ďe jaasiŇčkinaaki. Alla no Yi…ói mu√Ī√Īotoo…ďe …ďen"
  3,147,"Konngol ma…ď…ďe laataaki si wanaa wi'ugol: \"Joomi amen, haforan men junuubi amen e fantingol amen nder fiyaake amen, tabiŇčtinaa teppe amen, wallaa men e dow yim…ďe heefer…ďe …ďen"
  3,148,Alla Okki …ďe mbarjaari aduna ndin e mo∆ī∆īere mbarjaari laakara. Alla no Yi…ói mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen
  3,149,"Hey mon yo gom…óim…ďe, si on …óoftike …ďen heefer…ďe, …ďe ruttay on e batte [kaaferaaku] mon, waylito…óon ko on hayru…ďe(pertube)"
  3,150,"Si ko woni, ko Alla woni Gi…óo mon, ko KaŇčko woni mo∆ī∆īu…óo e walloo…ďe …ďe"
  3,151,"Arma Men Welloo kulol e nder …ďer…óe …ďen heefer…ďe, sabu ko …ďe kafidi Alla e kon ko O Jippinanaali hujja. Werde ma…ď…ďe ko ka yiite, bonii werde …ďen too√Īoo…ďe"
  3,152,"Gom…óii Alla Goonginanii on Fodoore Makko nden tuma nde warayno…óon …ďe e DuŇčayee Makko, haa nde cooy…óon lurru…óon e fiyaake …óen, yeddu…óon …ďaawo o hollii on ko yi…óu…óon. No e mon …ďen faalaa…ďe aduna, no e mon kadi …ďen faalaa…ďe laakara. Hooti O Yiili on e ma…ď…ďe fii yo O Ndaarndo on. Gom…óii O Yaafanike on. Alla ko Jom ∆Āural e dow gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  3,153,"Tuma nde dogayno…óon on ye∆ī∆īitoaako hay e gooto, Nulaa…óo on no noddira on …ďaawo mon. Suno e hoore suno he…ďi on fii wata on sunito e kon ko laawii on wanaa e kon ko he…ďi on. Alla ko Humpitii…óo e golloton"
  3,154,"Refti O Jippini e mo'on …ďaawo annde nden, hoolaare : ŇčoŇčre, hinde sudda fedde e mo'on ; fedde goo, pittaali ma…ď…ďe no aanini …ďe, hi…ďe sikka Alla ko wanaa goonga ; sikke yim…ďe majjere, hi…ďe wi'a: \"Hara no woodani men e fiyaake …óen go…ó…óum ?\" Maaku: \"Pellet, fiyaake …óen fow ko Alla woodani\". Hi…ďe suu…óa e pittaali ma…ď…ďe …óin ko …ďe fe√Ī√Īinantaa ma, hi…ďe wi'a: \"Si tawno no woodannoo men e fiyaake …óen go…ó…óum, men waretanooke …óoo\". Maaku: \"Hay si tawno on wonno ka cuu…ói mon, fee√Īayno …ďen …ďe Alla Winndi e dow mun maayde ka lelor…óe ma…ď…ďe\", e fii yo O La…ď…ďin ko woni …ďer…óe mon. Alla ko Anndu…óo ko woni e …ďer…óe"
  3,155,"Pellet, …ďen dogunoo…ďe e mo'on √Īalnde koneeli …óin …ói…ói fottunoo, anndu pellet, ko seytaane fergiti…ďe sabu yoga e ko …ďe faggitii. Gom…óii Alla Yaafike …ďe. Pellet, Alla ko Yaafotoo…óo Mu√Īoowo"
  3,156,"Hey mon yo gom…óim…ďe, wata on wa'u wa …ďen heefer…ďe …ďe wi'ani si…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen : \"Si …ďe yehii ka leydi, maa …ďe laatike ha…ďoo…ďe, si …ďe laatino ka amen goo, …ďe waretanooke\", ko fii yo Alla Wa…óir …óum …óon nimse ka …ďer…óe mo'on, Alla ko Rentu…óo ko golloton kon"
  3,157,"Hay si on wara e fii laawol Alla maa on maayii, ko yaafuyee immorde ka Alla e yurmeende …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko …ďe moo…ďata"
  3,158,"Si on maayii maa on waraama, pellet, ko ka Alla moo…ďete…óon"
  3,159,"Ko sabu yurmeende imoorde ka Alla newani…óaa …ďe. Si laatino sa…ótu…óo tikka …ďerndeejo, …ďe lancotono …ďe iwa takko maa. Yaafo …ďe insinano…óaa …ďe, diisino…óaa …ďe e fiyaake …óen. Si a fellitii, fawo e Alla. Pellet, Alla no Yi…ói fawotoo…ďe …ďen [e Makko]"
  3,160,"Si Alla Wallii on fooloowo on alaa., si O Hoynii on ko hommbo wallata on …ďaawo Makko? Ko e Alla woni ko gom…óim…ďe …ďen haani fawaade"
  3,161,"Laatanaaki Annabaajo woo nde o janfotoo. Kala janfii…óo o addoyay ko o janfii kon √Ďalnde Darngal.Hooti woŇčkii kala yo…ďee njo…ďdi ko ki faggitii, kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake"
  3,162,E ko on jokku…óo welayee Alla on wa'ata wa on hootidu…óo e tikkere immornde ka Alla kadi werde makko nden ko jahannama? nge bonii ruttorde
  3,163,"Kam…ďe ko …ďe darjaaji ka Alla, Alla ko ji*oowo ko …ďe gollata kon"
  3,164,"Gom…óii Alla Mo∆ī∆īike e gom…óim…ďe …ďen, tuma nde O Imminnoo e ma…ď…ďe Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, himo janngana …ďe Aayeeje Makko, himo la…ď…ďina …ďe, himo anndina …ďe Deftere nden e √Ďee√Īal ngal, hay si …ďe woniino adii nder majjere …ďanngunde"
  3,165,"E nde musiiba he…ďunoo on, gom…óii on he…ďiino yeru mun …ói…ói, wi'u…óon: \"No …óum woniri?!\" Maaku: \"∆äum ko immorde e pittaali mo'on\". Pellet, Alla ko Ha…ótan…óo kala huunde"
  3,166,"Ko he…ďi on kon √Īalnde dente …óen …ói…óe fottunoo, ko e DuŇčayee(sakkitoore) Alla, e fii no Alla Anndira gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  3,167,"e no O Anndira …ďen naafiqii…ďe, …ďe wi'anaa: \"Aree ha…ďon fii laawol Alla ngol maa du√Īon\". ∆Āe wi'i: \"Si me…óen anndunoo hare men jokkay on\". Kam…ďe nden √Īalnde, ko keeferaaku ngun …ďurnoo …ďa…ótaade e dii gom…ói…óal ngal : hi…ďe wowlira kunndule ma…ď…ďe ko alaa e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe. Ko Alla ∆Āuri Anndude ko …ďe soomi"
  3,168,"∆Āen wi'an…ďe si…ó…ďe mun, …ďe joo…óii: \"Si tawno …ďe …óoftino men, …ďe waretanooke\". Makku: \"Pottinee maayde nden e pittaali mo'on si on laatike goongu…ďe"
  3,169,"Wata a sikku …ďen waraa…ďe fii laawol Alla ngol ko maayu…ďe, ko woni: ko wuuru…ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe hi…ďe arsikee"
  3,170,"hi…ďe weltori ko Alla Okki …ďe kon e ∆Āural Makko, hi…ďe wewlira …ďen [si…ó…ďe] ma…ď…ďe …ďe …ďe hawraali e mu'un …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, wonnde kulol alanaa …ďe, wanaa kam…ďe woni ko sunoytoo"
  3,171,"Hi…ďe wewlira( weltoro) neema immorde ka Alla e …ďural. E wonnde pellet, Alla yeebataako njo…ďdi gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  3,172,"∆Āen nootii…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo on …ďaawo nde barmeere nden he…ďi …ďe. Hino woodani …ďen mo∆ī∆īin…ďe e ma…ď…ďe …ďe gom…ói, njo…ďdi mawndi"
  3,173,"∆Āen …ďe yim…ďe …ďen wi'annoo: \"Pellet yim…ďe …ďen moo…ďanike on, hulee…ďe\". ∆äum …ďeydi …ďe gom…óinal, …ďe wi': \"Alla yonii men, O mo∆ī∆īii yonndinoraa…óo"
  3,174,"∆Āe ruttodi e neema immorde ka Alla e …ďural, bone hewtaali …ďe, …ďe jokki yarluyee Alla on. Alla ko Jom-…ďural mawngal"
  3,175,"Anndee pellet, …óum mo'on ko seytaane : himo hul…ďinira …óum weldii…ďe makko …ďen. Wata on hulu …ďe, hulee Lam, si on laatike gom…óim…ďe"
  3,176,"Wata sunine …ďen yaccotoo…ďe e keeferaaku, pellet, …ďen lorrataa Alla hay huunde. Alla Yi…ói ko nde o waa-sata Wa…óannde ge…ďal ka laakara. No woodani …ďe lepte maw…óe"
  3,177,"Pellet, …ďen soktitorii…ďe keeferaaku ngun gom…óinal, …ďe lorrataa Alla hay huunde. Hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  3,178,"Wata …ďen yeddu…ďe sikku wonnde ko Men Nennirani …ďe kon ko mo∆ī∆īere pittaali …óin. Anndu pellet, ko Men Nennirani …ďe ko no …ďe …ďeydora bakkaatu. Hino woodani …ďe lepte hoynay…óe"
  3,179,"Laatanaaki Alla nde O Accata gom…óim…ďe …ďen e hoore ko won…óon e mun kon haa O Senndindira so…ďu…óo e laa…ďu…óo. Laatanaaki Alla kadi nde O ∆≥elliŇčta on e ko wirnii kon, si ko woni, Alla no Su…ďora e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen on mo O Muuyi. Gom…óinee Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, si on gom…óinii on gom…óii, hino woodani on njo…ďdi mawndi"
  3,180,"Wata …ďen wuddiroo…ďe ko Alla Okki …ďe kon e ∆Āural Makko sikku …óum ko mo∆ī∆īere wonannde …ďe. Si ko woni, …óum ko bone wonannde …ďe. Arma …ďe Ňčannanoye ko …ďe wuddiri kon √Ďalnde Darngal. Ko Alla woodani ndonndi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Alla ko Humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  3,181,"Gom…óii Allaahu on Nanii konngol …ďen wi'u…ďe: \"Alla ko baaso menen ko men al…óu…ďe!\". Arma Men winnda ko …ďe wowli kon e wargol …ďe ngol Annabaa…ďe …ďen ko aldaa e goonga, Men Daala: \"Mee…óee lepte sunna-royta"
  3,182,"∆äum wa…óirii sabu ko juu…óe mon …óen ardini kon. E wonnde pellet, Alla Wonaali Too√Īoowo jeyaa…ďe …ďen"
  3,183,"∆Āen wi'u…ďe: \"Alla Ahodii e amen wota men gom…óin Nulaa…óo woo haa on addana men …ďa…ótor…óum, yiite no √Īaama …óum\". Maaku: \"Gom…óii Nulaa…ďe goo ado am addaniino on …ďanngannduyeeji e kon ko wi'u…óon, e ko waran…óon …ďen si on laatike goognu…ďe"
  3,184,"Si …ďe fennii ma, gom…óii Nulaa…ďe goo ado maa fennanooma, …ďen adduno e ∆Āanngannduyeeji e ∆äeri e Deftere jalbuunde"
  3,185,"Kala woŇčkii mee…óay maayde. Pellet, ko on hunnaŇčtee…ďe njo…ďdiiji mon …óin √Ďalnde Darngal. Kala on pottinaa…óo e yiite ngen o naadaa Aljanna, gom…óii o malaama. Nguurda aduna …óam wonaali si wanaa dakammehun hodaykun"
  3,186,"Ma on jarribore jawle mon …óen e pittaali mon …óin, ma on nanir …ďen okkaa…ďe Defte …ďen ado moo…óo e …ďen sirku…ďe lorra …óu…óuka. Si on mu√Ī√Īike on gom…óii, pellet, anndee …óum, ko jeyaa…óum e pellite fiyakuuji"
  3,187,"JaŇčtii tuma nde Alla ∆≥ettunoo Ahadi e okkaa…ďe Deftere …ďen : \"Ma on …ďannginannde yim…ďe hara on suu…óaali nde\". ∆Āe werlii ndi …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe …ďe sodtitori ndi coggel pamarel! Bonii ko …ďe so…ótitori"
  3,188,"Wata sikke …ďen weltoray…ďe huunde nde …ďe okkaa, hi…ďe yi…ói nde …ďe yettirtee ko …ďe wa…óaali, wata sikku …ďen ko da…óay…ďe lepte …óen. Hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  3,189,Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Alla ko Hattan…óo kala huunde
  3,190,"Pellet, no e tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e luutondirgol jemma e √Īalorma ngol, ko Aayeeje wonannde …ďen haqqiloo…ďe"
  3,191,"∆Āen annditoo…ďe Alla ka …ďe darii e ka …ďe joo…óii e ka …ďe lelori becce ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe miijitoo fii tagu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin : \"Joomi amen, A Tagiraali …óum meere, senayee woodanii Ma, ∆äa…óndu men lepte yiite"
  3,192,"Joomo amen, pellet, An, Mo Naadu…óaa yiite, gom…óii A Hoynii mo. Alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen walloo…ďe"
  3,193,"Joomi amen, menen men nanii noddoowo no nodda e gom…óinal wonnde : \"Gom…óinee Joomi mon\", men gom…óini. Joomi amen, Haforan men junuubi amen, Motanaa men boneeji amen, mbarda men e ggu…ďe …ďen"
  3,194,"Joomi amen, Okku men ko Fodu…óaa men kon e dow Nulaa…ďe Maa …ďen, wata A Hoynu men √Ďalnde Darngal. Pellet, An A Lunndotaako fodoore"
  3,195,"Joomi ma…ď…ďe Jaabinani …ďe : Min Mi Yeebataa golle golloowo e moo…óon, woni gorko maa debbo, yoga e moo…óon iwde e yoga. ∆Āen fer…ďe yaltinaa ka galleeji mun,…ďe lorraa e Laawol Am ngol, …ďe ha…ďidaa …ďe waraa, ko pellet Min hafrat…ďe bon…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, e ko pellet Mi Naaday …ďe Aljanna …ói can…ói no ila e mun, …óum ko njo…ďdi immorde ka Alla, No ka Alla njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īundi. @Corrected"
  3,196,Wata hode yiltondirgol …ďen heefer…ďe ka leydi
  3,197,"dakammeyon pamaroy, hooti werde ma…ď…ďe nden ko jahannama, nge bonii nda…ó…óo"
  3,198,"Kono …ďen hulu…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe, hino woodani …ďe Aljannaaji, hino ila ley majji can…ói ; ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe nder majji, …óum ko jipporde immorde ka Alla. Ko woni ka Alla kon mo∆ī∆īani …óiggu…ďe …ďen. @Corrected"
  3,199,"Pellet, no e yim…ďe Defte …ďen, on gom…óin…óo Alla e ko Jippinaa e mon kon, e ko Jippinaa e ma…ď…ďe kon ; yaŇčkinanii …ďe Alla, …ďe wa…ótitirtaa Aayeeje Alla …óen coggeloy pamaroy. ∆Āen, hino woodani …ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, Alla ko Yaawu…óo √Īaawoore"
  3,200,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, mu√Ī√Īee, fooliron mu√Īal, tabiton, hulon Alla, belajo'o on maloyete"
  4,1,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe! Hulee Joomi mon On Tagu on immorde e woŇčkii wooti, O Tagi immorde e makki sonna makki, O Saaki immorde e …ďen …ói…óo wor…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe e rew…ďe. Hulee Alla On Mo naamnanirton sabu mun, [rento…óon kadi] e en…óammaaje …óen. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow mon Deenoowo"
  4,2,"Jonne wondu…ďe …ďen jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen. Wata on wa…ótitir so…ďe …óen ko laa…ďi. Wata on √Īaamu jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen [wa…óton …óum] e jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen. Pellet, …óum laatike bakkaatu maw…óo"
  4,3,"Si on hulee roŇčkugol nun…óude e wondu…ďe …ďen, resee ko laa…ďani on e rew…ďe, …ói…óo e tato e nayo. Si on hulii roŇčkugol nun…óude, wa…óee gooto maa …ďe jeyru…óon √Īaame mon ; ko …óum …ďuri …ďa…ótaade nde on too√Īu"
  4,4,"Jonniree rew…ďe …ďen teŇče ma…ď…ďe …óen dokkal. Si …ďe anniyanike on go…ó…óum e …óen [teŇče] e hoore laa…ďal woŇčkii, √Īaamee …óum, no newanii on …ďuu…ďani on"
  4,5,"Wata on jonnitu …óaye …ďen jawle mon …óen …óe Alla Wa…óirani on dartor…ďe. √Ďamminee …ďe e majje, holtinon …ďe, wowlanon …ďe konngol mo∆ī∆īol"
  4,6,"Ndaarndee wondu…ďe …ďen si …ďe yottike desal, si on so'ii e ma…ď…ďe peewal, jonnitee…ďe jawle ma…ďe …óen, wata on √Īaamir …óe faŇčtinngol e hawjugol …óoo yo …ďe mawnude. On taw…óo ko o galo, yo o naŇčto, on taw…óo ko o baaso, yo o √Īaamir no mo∆ī∆īiri. Si on jonnitii…ďe jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen, seedinee e dow ma…ď…ďe. Alla Yonii Hasboowo"
  4,7,"Hino woodani wor…ďe …ďen : ge…ďal immorde e kon ko neene e baaba acci e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen, hino woodani kadi rew…ďe …ďen : ge…ďal e kon ko neene e baaba acci e …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen ; …óuu…ói fam…ói e mun, ko ge…ďal farlaangal"
  4,8,"Si joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral en e wondu…ďe …ďen e waasu…ďe tawaama senndoore nden, okkoree…ďe e mun, wowlanon …ďe konngol mo∆ī∆īol"
  4,9,"Yo hulu …ďen, si tawno ko kam…ďe accunoo …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe ge…óal…ďe lo'u…ďe, …ďe hulana …ďen, yo …ďe hulu Alla …ďe wowla konngol sawaaba=peewngol"
  4,10,"Pellet, …ďen √Īaamiroo…ďe jawle yim…ďe …ďen e hoore too√Īee, pellet ko …ďe woni √Īaamude kon …ďe wa…óa e deedi ma…ď…ďe, ko yiite, arma …ďe naata hu…ď…ďunge"
  4,11,"Alla no Yamira on e fii …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen : hino woodani gorko yeru nge…óu rew…ďe …ói…óo. Si …ďe laatike rew…ďe …ďur…ďe …ói…óo, hino woodani …ďe tata…ďe …ói…ói e ko o acci. Si o laatike gooto, hino woodani mo feccere. Hino woodani neene e baaba makko gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe jeegobal, immorde e ko o acci, si tawii himo mari …ďi…ó…óo. Si o maraa …ďi…ó…óo, maw…ďe makko …ďen roni mo, hino woodani yumma makko tata…ďal. Si tawii himo mari neene-gootoo…ďe, hino woodani yumma makko jeega…ďal. ∆Āaawo siinugol wasiyee mo o wasiyii maa yo…ďugol √Īamaande nde o √Īawlinoo. Baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen e …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen, on anndaa ko hommbo e ma…ď…ďe …ďuri …ďadoraade on nafa. ∆äum ko farilla immorde ka Alla. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,12,"Hino woodani on feccere e ko rew…ďe mon acci, si tawii …ďe maraa …ďi…ó…óo. Si tawii hi…ďe mari …ďi…ó…óo, hino woodani on naya…ďal e kon ko …ďe aaci, …ďaawo siinugol wasiyee mo …ďe wasiyii maa yo…ďugol √Īamaande [ma…ď…ďe]. Hino woodani rew…ďe mon …ďen naya…ďal e kon ko accu…óon, si tawii …ďi…ó…óo alanaa on. Si tawii hi…óon mari …ďi…ó…óo, hino woodani …ďe jeetata…ďal e kon ko accu…óon, …ďaawo siinugol wasiyee mo wasiyi…óon maa yo…ďugol √Īamaande [mon]. Si wonii gorko no ronee rona-jala maa…óum debbo, hara himo mari neene-gooto gorko maa debbo, hino woodani kala ma…ď…ďe jeega…ďal. Si …ďe laatike …ďur…ďe …óum e …óuu…óude, kam…ďe ko hawtu…ďe ka tata…ďal, …ďaawo wasiyee wasiyaa…óo maa yo…ďugol √Īamaande nde wonaa lorraynde. ∆äum ko Wasiyee immorde ka Alla. Alla ko Anndu…óo Mu√Ī√Īii…óo"
  4,13,"∆äin ko Keeri Alla. Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, o naaday mo Aljannaaji, can…ói no ila e ley majji : ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton. Ko …óum woni malal mawngal. @Corrected"
  4,14,"Kala on yeddu…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, o jaggiti Keeri Makko …óin, O Naaday mo yiite nge o luttata e muu…óum ; hino woodani mo lepte hoynooje"
  4,15,"∆Āen huuwoo…ďe paŇčkare immorde e rew…ďe mon …ďen, seedinee e ma…ď…ďe nayo jeyaa…ďe e mo'on. Si …ďe seedike, jogitee…ďe ka cuu…ói haa maayde nden hunna …ďe, maa Alla Wa…óane …ďe laawol [yaltirngol]"
  4,16,"∆Āen …ói…óo huuwu…ďe fiju…ďe [paŇčkare …óen] e mo'on, lorree …ďen. Si …ďe tuubii …ďe mo∆ī∆īinii, …óuurno…óon e ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, Alla Laatike Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,17,"Anndee tuubuubuyee on ka Alla, ko wonannde …ďen golliroo…ďe bone sabu majjere, refti …ďe tuuba ka …ďadii. ∆Āen …óon, Alla Ja…ďanay …ďe tuubuubuyee. Alla Laatike Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,18,"Tuubuubuyee alanaa …ďen golliroo…ďe bone haa tuma maayde nden arani gooto e ma…ď…ďe o wi'a : \"Min mi tuubii jooni\", wanaa kadi …ďen maayoo…ďe hara kam…ďe ko …ďe heeferaa…ďe. ∆Āen …óon, Men Hebilanii …ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  4,19,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, dakantaako on nde ronirton rew…ďe …ďen doolugol, wata on laagu …ďe fii yo on he…ďtu yoga e ko okkuno…óon …ďe, si wanaa hara …ďe wa…óu paŇčkare …ďanngu…óo. Wonndiree e ma…ď…ďe no mo∆ī∆īiri. Si on a√Īii …ďe, hino jortaa nde a√Īoton huunde, Alla Wa…óa e mayre mo∆ī∆īere …óuu…óunde"
  4,20,"Si on yi…óii wa…ótitude debbo nokku debbo goo, hara hi…óon jonni go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe jawdi [heewundi], wata on ja…ďitu e mayri hay e huunde. E on ja…ďirayndi hoore bagamma e bakkaatu …ďanngu…óo"
  4,21,"Ko honno ∆īettirton ndi, gom…óii yoga e mon yottike e yoga, …ďe jogitike e mon ahadi tekkundi"
  4,22,"Wata on resu …ďen …ďe baabiraa…ďe mon resi e suddii…ďe si wanaa …óum ko fe∆ī∆īunoo. Pellet, …óum laatinoke paŇčkare e hutaare e bonnde laawol"
  4,23,"Harminanaama on : neeniraa…ďe mon …ďen, e jiw…ďe mon …ďen, e banndiraa…ďe mon …ďen, e yaayiraa…ďe mon …ďen, e neeniraa…ďe mon …ďen ka dewol, e jiw…ďe yumma gooto mon [gorko], e jiw…ďe banndiraawo mon, e neeniraa…ďe mon muynim…ďe on, e banndiraa…ďe mon …ďen ka muynan, e neeniraa…ďe …ďeynguuli mon, e njuttee…ďe mon won…ďe ka cuu…ói mon iw…ďe e …ďeynguuli mon …ďe naatidu…óon e suudu ; si tawii non on naatidaali e ma…ď…ďe suudu, bakkaatu fawaaki on [e resugol …ďen], e [rew…ďe] daganii…ďe …ďi…ó…ďe mon …ďen iw…ďe ka keeci, e nde moo…ďindirton hakkunde neene-gootoo…ďe …ói…óo, si wanaa …óum ko yawtunoo. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,24,"E saŇčii…ďe …ďen ka rew…ďe, si wanaa …ďen …ďe jeyru…óon ka √Īaame mon. ∆äum ko Farilla Alla e dow moo…óon. Daginanaama on ko woni …ďaawo …ďen …óon, nde …óa…ď…ďitor…ďe jawle mon hara ko on saŇčii…ďe wanaa on jinndoo…ďe. Kala mo dakmitor…óon e ma…ď…ďe desal : jonnitee…ďe teŇče ma…ď…ďe …óen. Ko farilla. Bakkaatu fawaaki e fii ko yarlondir…óon e mun …ďaawo farilla on. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,25,"Kala e moo…óon mo hattaaaki feere resugol seŇčii…ďe gom…óim…ďe, ko [resugol] …ďen …ďe jeytir…óon √Īaame mon, immorde e curbaa…ďe mon gom…óim…ďe. Alla no Anndai gom…óinal mon ngal. Yoga e mon ko e yoga Resiree…ďe duŇčayee yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, jonniron …ďe teŇče ma…ď…ďe …óen no mo∆ī∆īiri. SaŇčii…ďe hara wanaa jinndoo…ďe njaatoo. Si …ďe seaŇčike …ďe addii paŇčkare, no fawii …ďe feccere ko fawii saŇčii…ďe rim…ďe …ďen e lepte. ∆äum, ko fii on hulu…óo e mo'on yanugol e jeeno. Ko nde mu√Ī√Īoto…óon …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on. Alla Haforoowo Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,26,"Allaahu On no Faandii ∆Āannginanngol on O Fewna on e laawi …ďeya adinoo…ďe on, O Ja…ďana on tuubuubuyee. Alla ko Anndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,27,"Alla no Faala nde O Ja…ďaŇčta on tuubuubuyee, …ďen jokku…ďe mbelee…óe faalaa nde oo√Īorton oo√Īannde mawnde"
  4,28,"Alla no Yi…ói Hayfinanta on, ne…ó…óaŇčke tagaama ko o lo'u…óo"
  4,29,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, wata on √Īaamir jawle mon …óen hakkunde moo…óon e mehre, si wanaa hara ko e njulaaku ngu wela…óon e muu…óum. Wata on waru pittaali mon …óin. Pellet, Alla Laatike Hinnotoo…óo on"
  4,30,"kala huuwu…óo …óum e hoore ngaynu e too√Īe, aray Men Naada mo yiite : …óum laatike newanii…óum Alla"
  4,31,"Si on wo…ó…óitike [bakkaatu] maw…ói …ói ha…óa…óon …óin e mun, Men Heefanay on boneeji mon …óin, Men Naadira e naatirgal teddungal"
  4,32,"Wata on yelo ko Alla ∆Āurniri yoga e mon dow yoga. Hino woodani wor…ďe …ďen ge…ďal immorde e ko …ďe faggitii kon, hino woodani kadi rewbe bege…ďal immorde e kon ko …ďe faggitii. Tororee Alla immorde e ∆Āural Makko. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  4,33,"Wonannde kala Men Wa…óanii …óum ronoo…ďe [heftu…ďe] e …óum ko jibim…ďe …ďen acci, e …ďadondiraa…ďe ; e …ďen …ďe ahoduno…óon e mun : jonnee…ďe ge…ďal ma…ď…ďe ngal. Pellet, Alla Laatike ko O Seedii…óo e kala huunde"
  4,34,"Wor…ďe …ďen ko √Īii…ďu…ďe [e daŇčkiitagol] rew…ďe …ďen, sabu ko Alla ∆Āurniri kon yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore yoga, e sabu kon ko wintii e jawle ma…ď…ďe. [rew…ďe] mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen, ko yaŇčkinii…ďe reenotoo…ďe ka wirnii, sabu kon ko Alla Reenini …ďe.∆Āen [rew…ďe] …ďe huloton dartagol(cuwtagol) mun : waajee…ďe, feron…ďe ka nda…ó…óudiiji, piyon…ďe. Si …ďe …óoftike on, wata on a…ď…ďir e dow ma…ď…ďe laawol ! Pellet, Alla Laatike Toowu…óo, Maw…óo"
  4,35,"Si on hulii lurral hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, imminee √Īaawoowo immor…óo ka yim…ďe gorko on e √Īaawoowo immor…óo ka yim…ďe debbo on. Si …ďe faandike mo∆ī∆īinngol, Alla Hawrindinay hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo, Humpitii…óo"
  4,36,"Rewee Alla wata on kafidu e Makko hay huunde. Jibim…ďe on …ďen mo∆ī∆īo…óon e ma…ď…ďe, e joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral'en, e wondu…ďe …ďen, e waasu…ďe …ďen, e kawtaljo jom-…ďadondiral, e kawtal baŇčŇče, e wonndi…ó…óo baŇčŇče, e …ďii laawol, e …ďen …ďe jeyru…óon √Īaame mon. Pellet, Alla Yi…óaa kala on laatii…óo √Īaa∆īoowo mantotoo…óo"
  4,37,"∆Āen …ďe no wudda, …ďe yamira yim…ďe …ďen nguddam, …ďe suu…óa kon ko Alla okki …ďe e ∆Āural Makko. Men Maranii heefer…ďe …ďen lepte hoynooje"
  4,38,"E …ďen …ďe no nafqira jawle mun …óen ka yiinorgol yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe gom…óiŇčtaa Alla wanaa √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde nden. Kala on mo seytaane wonani …óum ciŇčkotaa…óo : haray o bonii ciŇčkodaa…óo"
  4,39,E ko hon…óum fawinoo …ďe si …ďe gom…óinno Alla e √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde nden …ďe nafqi e kon ko Alla Arsike …ďe ? Alla Laatike Anndu…óo …ďe
  4,40,"Pellet, Alla Too√Īirtaa yeru jarra-hun, si wonii ko mo∆ī∆īere, O Soway nde, O Okka immorde ka Mokko njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,41,"Ko honno si tawii Men Addoyii immorde e kala mofte seeditotoo…óo, Men Adde e dow …ďee …óoo ko a seeditotoo…óo"
  4,42,"Nden √Ďalnde, heefer…ďe …ďn e yeddu…ďe …ďen Nulaa…óo on yeloto hara nun …ďe fonndeteno e leydi ndin, …ďe suu…óataa Alla yeewtere"
  4,43,"Ko onon yo gim…óim…ďe, wata on …ďa…óto julde den hara ko on siwru…ďe haa anndon ko wowloton ; wanaa ka moddu…óon e lonngal, si wanaa hara ko on ta∆īitoo…ďe laawol haa la…ď…ďino…óon. Si on laatike nawnu…ďe, maa hi…óon e hoore jahal, maa …ďaawo hoggo arii go…ó…óo e mon(yaadon dow wuro), maa on soccondirii e rew…ďe …ďen on he…ďaali ndiyam, taamoree mbullaari(leydi) laa…ďundi : mowlon geece mon …óen e juu…óe mon …óen. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo Yawtanoowo"
  4,44,"E a yi'aali faade e …ďen okkaa…ďe ge…ďal e …óefte …óen, hi…ďe sooda majjere nden, hi…ďe faalaa nde majjoton laawol [foccondirngol] ngol"
  4,45,"Ko Alla ∆Āuri Anndude ay…ďe mon …ďen. Alla yonii Gi…óo, Alla yonii Ballo"
  4,46,"Hino e …ďeya alyahuudaa…ďe wayloo…ďe konngol ngol e nokku maggol …ďe wi'a: \"Men nanii men yeddii ; he…óo ko wanaa nannatee…óo, aynu men\", ka hallugol …óem…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e yuwugol ka diina. Hara nun …ďe wi'ayno : \"Men nanii men …óoftike nanu ndaaraa\", ko …óum …ďuraynoo mo∆ī∆īannde …ďe, …ďura foccaade. Ko woni tun, Alla Hu…óirii …ďe geddi ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe gom…óiŇčtaa si wanaa see…óaa"
  4,47,"Ko onon yo …ďeya okkanoo…ďe Defte, gom…óinee nden nde Men Jippini googinnde …óen won…óe ka mon, ado Men Mehude geece [mon …óen] Men Ruttira…óe …ďabbe majje, maa Men Hu…óira …ďe wano Men Hu…óirnoo non yim…ďe asewe …ďen. Fiyaake Alla on Laatke LaatiŇčtee…óum"
  4,48,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidoowo Mo e go…ó…óum, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi …óum wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafidu…óo Alla e go…ó…óum, gom…óii o fepandiima bakkaatu maw…óo"
  4,49,"E a yi'aali …ďen …ďe no la…ď…ďina pittaali ma…ď…ďe ? Ko woni, Ko Alla La…ď…ďiŇčta on Mo O Muuyi, …ďe too√Īoytaake yeru gurun tamaro"
  4,50,Ndaarii ko hol no …ďe woni fefindoraade e Alla fenaade ! ∆äum …óon yonii bakkaatu fee√Īu…óo
  4,51,"E a yi'aali faade e …ďen okkanoo…ďe ge…ďal ka Deftere, hi…ďe gom…óina ndaaro e bewinay…ói …óin, hi…ďe wi'ana …ďen heefer…ďe : \"Ko …ďee …óoo …ďuri feewude laawol e dii …ďeya gom…óime"
  4,52,"Ko …ďen woni …ďe Alla Hu…ói …ďen, kala mo Alla Hu…ói, a he…ďaŇčtaa mo ballo"
  4,53,"Kaa woodam…ďe ge…ďal immorde e laamu ? Ountuma, …ďe okkataano yim…ďe …ďen yeru hufol tamaro"
  4,54,"Kaa …ďe a√Īay yim…ďe …ďen e ko Alla Okki …ďe kon e ∆Āural Makko ? Gom…óii Men Okkii …ďeynguure Ibraahiima nden Deftere e Faltaare, Men Okki …ďe Laamu Mawngu"
  4,55,"Hino e ma…ď…ďe on gom…óin…óo nde, no e ma…ď…ďe kadi on faddii…óo nde. Jahannama yonii hu…ď…ďaynge"
  4,56,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, aray Men Naada …ďe yiite : tuma kala guri ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďenndi, Men Wa…ótitana …ďe guri goo fii no …ďe mee…óira lepte …óen. Pellet, Alla Laatike Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,57,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, aray Men Naada …ďe Aljannaaji …ói no ila e ley majji can…ói, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ndeer ton poomaa hino woodani …ďe ton rew…ďe la…ď…ďinaa…ďe Men Naada …ďe …óowdi duumiindi. @Corrected"
  4,58,"Pellet, Alla no Yamira on tottoton koolaaje …óen faade e yim…ďe majje …ďen, e si on √Īaaway hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen nde √Īaawirton nun…óal. Pellet, ko Alla Waajorta on kon labaama. Pellet, Alla Laatike Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  4,59,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, …óoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on e joomiraa…ďe yamiroore …ďen e moo…óon. Si on poo…óondirii e huunde, ruttee nde ka Alla e ka Nulaa…óo on, si on laatike gom…óim…ďe Alla e √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde nden. Ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude …ďuri labeede battane"
  4,60,"E a yi'aali …ďen …ďe no aa∆īoo wonnde kam…ďe …ďe gom…óinii kon ko Jippinaa e maa…óa e kon ko Jippinaa ado maa…óa? Hi…ďe faalaa nde …ďe √Īaawinoytoo ka bewinay…ói …óin, gom…óii le …ďe yamiraama nde …ďe yeddata …ói. Seytaane non hino faalaa majjinnde …ďe majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  4,61,"Si …ďe wi'anaama : \"Aree faade e kon ko Alla Jippini e faade e Nulaa…óo on\", a yi'ay naafiqi en no faddoo e maa…óa faddagol"
  4,62,"Ko honno [wonirta] si tawii musiiba he…ďirii …ďe sabu ko …ďe ardiniri juu…óe ma…ď…ďe, refti …ďe ara e maa…óa hi…ďe woondira Alla : \"Men faandaaki si wanaa mo∆ī∆īinngol e hawrinndinal"
  4,63,"Ko …ďen woni …ďe Alla Anndi ko woni ndeer …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, …óuurno gaay ma…ď…ďe, waajo…óaa …ďe, wowolanna …ďe konngol yottotongol ka pittaali ma…ď…ďe"
  4,64,"Men Nuliraali Nulaa…óo [woo] si wanaa fii yo o …óofte e DuŇčayee Alla. Hara nun tuma …ďe too√Īunoo pittaali ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe aruno ma …ďe insinii e Alla, Nulaa…óo on insinanii …ďe, …ďe tawayno Alla ko Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee, jumotoodo"
  4,65,"Hey, Mi Woondirii Joomi maa…óa, …ďe gom…óiŇčtaa haa …ďe √Īaawinora maa huunde ko yani hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, refti …ďe he…ďataa …ďitteende ka pittaali ma…ď…ďe e kon ko √Īaawu…óaa, …ďe jebbiloo jebbilagol"
  4,66,"Hara nun Men Farluno e ma…ď…ďe wonnde : \"Waree pittaali mon …óin\", maa \"yalton e galleeji mon\", …ďe wa…óataano …óum si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Sinno kam…ďe …ďe huuwuno kon ko …ďe waajoranoo, …óum laatotono mo∆ī∆īere wonannde …ďe, …ďura tii…óude kadi tabital"
  4,67,"nden tuma, Men Okkayno …ďe immorde ka Amen, njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,68,Men Fewnayno …ďe laawol focciingol
  4,69,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo on : …ďen …óon wonndoyay e …ďen …ďe Alla Neemini immorde e Annabaa…ďe, e goongu…ďe, e sahiddinnoo…ďe, e mo∆ī∆īube. ∆Āen …óon mo∆ī∆īii wonndii…ďe"
  4,70,"Ngal …óon ∆Āural ko immorde ka Alla, Alla Yonii Anndu…óo"
  4,71,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, jogitee reŇčtor…ói mon …óin, runnjon ko on sertu…ďe maa runnjon on rentu…ďe"
  4,72,"Hino e mo'on on nennotoo…óo, si musiiba he…ďii on, o wi'a : \"Gom…óii Alla Neeminii e am, nde tawnoo mi laatodanooki e ma…ď…ďe ceedii…óo"
  4,73,"Si tawii he…ďii on ∆Āural immorde ka Alla, ma o wi'a wa si tawii mee…óaali laataade hakkunde mon giggol : \"Ee jalla am si mi tawdano e ma…ď…ďe ! Mi malee malal mawngal"
  4,74,"Yo ha…ďide fii laawol Alla ngol, …ďen …ďe no sooditira guurdam aduna …óam laakara on ! Kala on ha…ďidaa…óo fii laawol Alla ngol o waraa maa o fooli, arma Men Okka mo njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,75,"E ko he…ďi on, on ha…ďidetaake fii laawol Alla ngol ? e Lo'inaa…ďe …ďen ka wor…ďe, e ka rew…ďe, e ka fay…ďe, …ďen …ďe no wi'a: \"Joomi amen, Yaltin men e ndee saare nde yim…ďe mun too√Īi, Wa…óanaa men immorde ka Maa…óa gi…óo, Wa…óanaa Men immorde ka Maa…óa ballo"
  4,76,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe hino ha…ďidee fii laawol Alla ngol, …ďeya heefer…ďe hino ha…ďidee e laawol …ďewnay…ói …óin. Ha…ďee weldii…ďe seytaane …ďen : pellet, pewje seytaane …óen laatike lo'u…óe"
  4,77,"E a yi'aali …ďen wi'ananoo…ďe : \"Suree juu…óe mon …óen, √Īimnon julde, jonnon asakal\". Tuma hare nden farlanoo e ma…ď…ďe, e jaka fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe hino hulira yim…ďe …ďen wano Alla hulirtee, maa ko …ďuri tii…óude e kulol, …ďe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, ko hon…óum Farla…óaa e dow amen hare ? Ko ha…ónoo Nennitanaa men …óum haa e lajal …ďadiingal ?\" Maaku : \"Dakamme aduna on ko see…óa, ko laakara on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on hul…óo [Alla], on too√Īetaake yeru hufol tamara"
  4,78,"Nokku woo ka laati…óon maayde nden hewtitoto on, hay si on laatike e nder tataaji mahaa…ói. Si mo∆ī∆īere he…ďii …ďe, …ďe wi'a: \"∆äum …óoo ko immorde ka Alla\" Si bone he…ďii …ďe, …ďe wi'a :\"∆äum …óoo ko immorde e maa…óa !\" Maaku: \"Kala majji ko immorde ka Alla\". E ko nanngi …ďee yim…ďe …ďe …ďattitaako faamude yeewtere"
  4,79,"Huunde woo ko he…ďu maa e mo∆ī∆īere ko immorde ka Alla, huunde woo ko he…ďu maa e bone ko immorde e woŇčkii maa kin. Men Nulii ma wonannde yim…ďe …ďen Nulaa…óo. Alla Yonii Seede"
  4,80,"Mo …óoftike Nulaa…óo on gom…óii o …óoftike Alla. Mo huccitii, Men Nulaali ma e dow ma…ď…ďe reenoowo"
  4,81,"Hi…ďe wi'a: \"∆äoftaare!\", si …ďe yaltii ka maa…óa, fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe waaliday [e miijo goo] ko woori kon ko maaku…óaa. Alla no Winnda kon ko waalidata e mun. ∆äuurno …ďe fawo…óaa e Alla. Alla Yonii Hoolor…óo"
  4,82,"E …ďee taskitortaa Qur'aana on ? Sinno nde iwru-nde ko wanaa ka Alla, …ďe tawayno e mayre lurre …óuu…óu…óe"
  4,83,"Si arii …ďe e fiyaake immorde e hoolaare, maa kulol, …ďe lollina …óum. Sinno …ďe ruttuno …óum e Nulaa…óo on e …ďen fewjoo…ďe fii ma…ď…ďe, …ďen …ďullitay…ďe e ma…ď…ďe anndayno …óum. Si wanaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, on jokkayno seytaane si wanaa see…óaa…ďe"
  4,84,"Ha…ďu fii laawol Alla ngol, a fawaaka si wanaa hoore-maa. Rer…óin gom…óim…ďe …ďen, arma Alla nde Surata doole heefer…ďe …ďen. Ko Alla …ďuri Sa…ótude doole, ko KaŇčko …ďuri Sa…ótude muusnugol"
  4,85,"Kala on tefu…óo tefoore labaande wonay mo ge…ďal e mayre, kala kadi on tefu…óo tefoore bonnde wonany mo e mayre ge…ďal. Alla Laatike Hattan…óo kala huunde"
  4,86,"Si on hiwroraama hiwraango, hiwritoree ko …ďuri ngon …óon maa rutton ngo. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow kala huunde ko O Hasboowo"
  4,87,"Alla, rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko, ma O Moo…ďitoy on √Ďalnde Darngal, sikke alaa e Mayre. E ko hombo …ďuri goongude Alla yeewtere"
  4,88,"Ko wa…ói on e fii …ďee naafiqii…ďe feddeeji …ói…ói ?! Ko Alla woni Uggin…óo …ďe sabu ko …ďe faggitii. E on faala fewnude on mo Alla Majjini ? Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a he…ďantaa mo laawol"
  4,89,"Hi…ďe yeloo sinno on yeddayno wano …ďe yeddiri non, laato…óon fotoo…ďe. Wata on jogito e ma…ď…ďe weldii…ďe haa …ďe fera e laawol Alla ngol. Si …ďe huccitii, nanngee …ďe waron …ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe.Wata on jogito e ma…ď…ďe weldi…ó…óo wanaa ballo"
  4,90,"Si wanaa …ďen …ďe hino jokkoo faade e yim…ďe …ďe ahadi woni hakkunde mon e ma…ď…ďe, maa…óun …ďe arii on …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen no …ďi…ótanii ha…ďugol on, maa ha…ďugol yim…ďe …ďen. Si Alla Haajuno, O Wurtayno …ďe e dow moo…óon, …ďe ha…ďa on. Si …ďe pottitike on, …ďe ha…ďaali on, …ďe werlike kisal e mon, haray Alla Wa…óanaali on e dow ma…ď…ďe laawol"
  4,91,"Arma tawon wo…ó…ďe goo faandii…ďe nde …ďe holnora on …ďe holnora yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen. Tuma kala nde …ďe ruttitaa e geddi …óin,…ďe su∆ī∆īitee e nder majji. Si …ďe pottitaaki on, …ďe werloo kisal e mon, …ďe suri juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, nanngee …ďe waron …ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe. Ko …ďen …óon moo…óon, [woni ke Men] Wa…óani on e ma…ď…ďe hujja …ďanngu…óo"
  4,92,"Haananaa gom…óin…óo nde o warata gom…óin…óo si wanaa [hara ko] faljere. On war…óo gom…óin…óo, yo rin…óin daande gom…óinnde e diya jonnetee…óo yim…ďe makko …ďen : si wanaa hara …ďen sakkii. Si wonii ko jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe ay…ďe mon, hara kaŇčko ko o gom…óin…óo, ko rin…óingol daande gom…óinnde. Si wonii ko jeyaa…óo e yim…ďe …ďe ahadi woni hakkunde mon e ma…ď…ďe, ko diya jonnetee…óo yim…ďe makko …ďen, e rin…óingol daande gom…óinnde. On mo hebaali ko : hoorugol lebbi …ói…ói jokkondir…ói tuubuubuyee immorde ka Alla. Alla Laatike Anndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,93,"Kala war…óo gom…óin…óo e hoore tewagol, njo…ďdi makko ndin ko Jahannama, luttoowo e nder magge ; Alla Tikkanii mo, O Hu…óii mo, O Hebilanii mo lepte maw…óe"
  4,94,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, si on yahii e laawol Alla, …ďannginee [tefon] wata on wi'an on werlii…óo e mon kisal : \"Wanaa a gom…óin…óo\", hi…óon …óa…ď…ďa jawdi nguurdam aduna, ko ka Alla konhoyri …óuu…óundi woni. Ko wano non laatorno…óon ko adii, Alla Neemini e mon. ∆Āannginee. Pellet, Alla Laatike Humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  4,95,"Gom…óim…ďe joo…óii…ďe …ďen, hara wanaa joomiraa…ďe lorra …ďen, fotataa e …ďen tii…ónortoo…ďe e laawol Alla ngol jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen e woŇčkiiji ma…ďe …óin. Alla ∆Āurnirii tii…ónor…ďe jawle mun …óen e woŇčkiiji mun …óin, e dow joo…ďii…ďe …ďen, darja. ∆Āe fow ma…ď…ďe Alla Fodii …ďe mo∆ī∆īere, Alla ∆Āurnirii tii…ónotoo…ďe …ďen e dow joo…óii…ďe …ďen njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,96,"Darjaaji immorde ka Makko, e haforanal, e Hinnayee. Alla Laatike Hafroowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,97,"Pellet, …ďen …ďe Malaa'ika en no warata, hara ko …ďe too√Īu…ďe pittaali ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe wi'a : \"Ko e hon…óum wonuno…óon ?!\". ∆Āe wi'a : \"Men laatinoke lo'inanoo…ďe ka leydi\". ∆Āe wi'a : \"Leydi Alla ndin laatanooki yaajundi hanno feron e mayri ?\". ∆Āen …óon, werde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,98,"Si wanaa …ďen lo'inaa…ďe immorde ka wor…ďe, e ka rew…ďe, e ka sukaa…ďe …ďe hattanaa yahdu, …ďe feewataa e laawol"
  4,99,"∆Āen …óon, arma Alla Yaafanoo …ďe. Alla Laatike Yaafotoo…óo, Haforoowo"
  4,100,"Kala feru…óo e laawol Alla ngol o taway ka leydi yol…óere …óuu…óunde e yaajeende. Kala yaltu…óo e suudu mu'un ko o feru…óo faade e Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, hooti maayde nden hewtitii mo, gom…óii njo…ďdi makko ndin tabitii ka Alla. Alla Laatike Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,101,"Si on jinndii ka leydi, haray bakkaatu fawaaki on nde ustoton julde nden, si on hulii nde yeddu…ďe …ďen fitiŇčta on. Pellet, heefer…ďe …ďen laatanike on ay…ďe fee√Īu…ďe"
  4,102,"Si a tawdaama e ma…ď…ďe a darnanii …ďe julde, yo fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe darodo e maa…óa yo …ďe jogito jogaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin ; si …ďe sujjii, yo …ďe wonu …ďaawo mon, yo fedde ndeya nde juulaali aru, yo …ďe juulidu e maa…óa yo …ďe jogito reetor…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin e jogaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Yeddu…ďe …ďen yelinoke sinno on welsindotono gaay e jogaaji mon …óin e doŇčle mon …óen, …ďe oo√Īoo e moo…óon oo√Īannde wootere. Bakkaatu fawaaki on si …óon wonndi e lorra immorde e to…ďo, maa on laatike nawnu…ďe nde walliŇčton jogaaji mon …óin. Jogitee reŇčtor…ói mon …óin. Pellet, Alla Hebilanii heefer…ďe …ďen lepte hoynooje"
  4,103,"Si on gaynii julde nden, jaŇčtoree Alla e darnnde, e jonnde e ka hoore becce mon. Si on dee∆īii, √Īi…ďnee julde nden. Pellet, julde nden laatike e gom…óim…ďe …ďen farill hee∆īaa [waqiŇčtinaa]"
  4,104,"Wata on lo*u e nder …óa…ď…ďitugol yim…ďe …ďen. Si on laatike hi…óon naawee, kam…ďe kadi hi…ďe naawiree wano naawirte…óon, hi…óon jortii immorde e Alla ko …ďe jortaaki. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,105,Menen Men Jippinirii Deftere nden e maa…óaa e hoore goonga fii yo a √Īaawir hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen kon ko Alla Hollu maa. Wata on wonan janfotoo…ďe …ďen wennjanoowo
  4,106,"Insino e Alla. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,107,"Wata a wennjondire fii …ďen janfotoo…ďe pittaali mun. Pellet, Alla Yi…óaa on janfotoo…óo, bakkondin…óo"
  4,108,"Hi…ďe suu…óoo yim…ďe …ďen …ďe suu…óotaako Alla, Himo Wonndi e ma…ď…ďe tuma …ďe waalaynoo fewjude kon ko O Welaaka e konngol. Alla Laatike Hu…ďindii…óo kon ko …ďe gollata"
  4,109,"Hey mon yo …ďe'e on wennjii fii ma…ď…ďe e …óam nguurdam aduna, e ko hommbo wennjoyta Alla fii ma…ď…ďe √Ďalnde Darngal, kaa ko hommbo laatanoytoo…ďe fawtii…óo"
  4,110,"Kala on gollu…óo bone maa o too√Īi hoore makko, hooti o insinii e Alla, o taway Alla ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,111,"Kala kadi faggitii…óo bakkaatu, pellet, ko e hoore makko o woni faggitaade …óum. Alla Laatike Anndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,112,"Kala faggitii…óo goopol maa bakkaatu hooti o bugii …óum e hoore da…óndii…óo, gom…óii o ronnditike fenaande e bakkaatu …ďanngu…óo"
  4,113,"Si wanaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow maa…óa e Yurmeende Makko nden, fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe himmirayno majjinngol ma, …ďe alaa e majjinnde si wanaa pittaali ma…ď…ďe …óin, …ďe lorrirtaama hay e huunde. Alla Jippinii e maa…óa Deftere nden e √Ďee√Īal ngal, O Anndinii ma huunde nden a anndaano. ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow maa…óa laatike mawnungal"
  4,114,"Mo∆ī∆īere alaa e ko heewi e yeewtere ma…ď…ďe nden, si wanaa on yamir…óo sadaka, maa mo∆ī∆īere maa mo∆ī∆īiŇčtingol hakkunde yim…ďe …ďen. Kala wa…óir…óo …óum …óa…ď…ďugol welayee Alla, arma Men Okka mo njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,115,"Kala on lunndii…óo Nulaa…óo on …ďaawo nde paawal ngal …ďanngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gom…óim…ďe …ďen, Men HucciŇčtinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, Men Naadoya mo Jahannanma, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidugol Mo e go…ó…óum, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi …óum wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafidu…óo Alla e go…ó…óum, gom…óii o majjii majjere wo…ó…óiinde"
  4,117,"∆Āe alaa e rewude ko woori Alla, si wanaa [sanamuuji] rew…óinaa…ói, …ďe alaa e rewude si wanaa seytaane sanndal…óiin…óo"
  4,118,"Alla Hu…óii ndu, ndu wi'i : \"Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaa…ďe maa …ďen ge…ďal farlaangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinoy…ďe, ma mi yelinoy…ďe, ma mi yamiroy…ďe, ma …ďe ta∆īu noppi neemoraa…ói …óin, ma mi yamir…ďe, ma …ďe waylu tagu Alla ngun !\". Kala jogitii…óo seytaane gi…óo ko woori Alla, gom…óii o hayrii hayrere …ďanngunde"
  4,120,"Himo foda …ďe himo yelina …ďe, seytaane fodaali …ďe si wanaa hodo"
  4,121,"∆Āen …óon wemoolorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Jahannama, …ďe he…ďirtaa nge da…óirde"
  4,122,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, aray Men Naada …ďe Aljannaaji …ói no ila e ley majji can…ói : ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe nder ton poomaa. Fodoore Alla nde ko goonga. Ko hommbo …ďuri Alla goongude konngol ? @Corrected"
  4,123,"Wonaali ko yelaaji mon …óin wanaa yelaaji jom…ďe Defte …ďen. Kala gollu…óo bone o yo…ďete …óum, o he…ďanoytaake ko woori Alla gi…óo wanaa ballo"
  4,124,"Kala gollu…óo immorde e mo∆ī∆īi …óin, fota ko gorko maa ko debbo, hara ko o gom…óin…óo, …ďen …óon naatay Aljanna …ďe too√Īetaake yeru gurun [tamaro]"
  4,125,"Alaa …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude diina haa hewti on jebbil…óo yeeso mun ngon Alla, hara ko o mo∆ī∆īin…óo, o rewi laawol Ibraahiima ruu…óii…óo. Alla Jogitike Ibraahiima gi…óo"
  4,126,Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike Hu…ďindii…óo kala huunde
  4,127,"Hi…ďe lamdo maa fii rew…ďe …ďen, maaku : \"Alla no saggitude on fii …ďen [rew…ďe], e kon ko jaŇčngetee e dow moo…óon ka Deftere fii …ďen rew…ďe wondu…ďe, …ďen …ďe on jonnataa kon ko …ďe farlanaaa, hi…óon rer…óa fii resugol …ďe, e …ďen lo'inaa…ďe immorde ka fay…ďe, e nde daraŇčto…óon wondu…ďe …ďen nun…óal. Kala ko huuwoton e mo∆ī∆īere, pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo …óum"
  4,128,"Si wonii debbo hulirii moodi makko suwtaade suwtaade maa …óuurnaare, bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe nde …ďe mo∆ī∆īiŇčtinirta hakkunde ma…ď…ďe sulhu.Ko sulhu on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, pittaali …óin tawdaama ndeereraaku.Si on mo∆ī∆īinii on gom…óii, pellet Alla Laatike Humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  4,129,"On waawataa nun…óude hakkunde rew…ďe …ďen hay si on rer…óii. Wata tun on oo√Īo kala oo√Īannde, accon mo wa yowaa…óo. Si on mo∆ī∆īinii on gom…óii, pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,130,"Si …ďe sertii, Alla Al…óiniroyay kala ma…ď…ďe immorde e Yaajeende Makko nden. Alla Laatike Yaaju…óo […ďural], √Ďee…óu…óo"
  4,131,"Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli kon e ka leydi. Gom…óii Men Ahodinoke e …ďeya okkaa…ďe Defte ado mon, e onon : \"Hulee Alla !\". Si on yeddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike Galo, Yettinii…óo"
  4,132,Ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Yonii Fawtii…óo
  4,133,"Si O Muuyii, O Na…ďay on, onon yo yim…ďe, O Adda wo…ó…ďe goo. Alla Laatike Hattan…óo e dow …óum"
  4,134,"Kala taw…óo no faandii mbarjaari aduna, ko ka Alla mbarjaari aduna e laakara woni. Alla Laatike Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  4,135,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, √Īii…ďu…ďe e nun…óal seedan- …ďe Alla, hay si ko e dow pittaali mon, maa jinnaa…ďe mon …ďen maa …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen. Si wonii ko o galo maa…óum baaso, ko Alla ∆Āuri Haanndude e ma…ď…ďe. Wata on jokku mbelee…óe, nde nun…óoton. Si on waylii maa on …óuurnike, pellet, Alla Laatike Humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  4,136,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, gom…óinee Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, e Deftere nde O Jippini e Nulaa…óo Makko on, e …óen Defte …óe O Jippini ko adii. Kala yeddu…óo Alla, e Malaa'ikaa…ďe Makko …ďen, e Defte Makko …óen, e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen e √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde nden, gom…óii o majjii majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  4,137,"Pellet, …ďen gom…óim…ďe, hooti …ďe yeddi, hooti …ďe gom…óini, hooti …ďe yeddi, hooti …ďe …ďeydorii keeferaaku, Alla Laatoraali Yawtanoowo …ďe wanaa O Fewnoowo …ďe e laawol"
  4,138,"Wewlinir naafiqii…ďe …ďen, wonnde no woodani lepte muusu…óe"
  4,139,"∆Āen …ďe no jogitoo heefer…ďe …ďen yi…ó…ďe ko wanaa gom…óim…ďe …ďen, e …ďe …óa…ď…ďay e juu…óe ma…ď…ďe teddungal ? Pellet, teddungal ngal fow ko Alla Heeranii"
  4,140,"Gom…óii O Jippinii e mon ka nder Deftere Si on nanii Aayeeje Alla …óen no yeddee …óe jalikitee, wata on joo…óodu e ma…ď…ďe haa …ďe jumpana yewtere goo ko woori nden …óon, si on wa…óii …óum on fotii e ma…ď…ďe\". Pellet, Alla ko Moo…ďoyoowo naafiqii…ďe …ďen e heefer…ďe …ďen ka Jahannama …ďe denndaangal"
  4,141,"∆Āen habbitantoo…ďe on, si uddital laatanike on immorde ka Alla, …ďe wi'a : \"E, men wonndaano e mo'on ?\", Si ge…ďal laatanike heeferaa…ďe …ďen, …ďe wi'a : \"E men foolinaano e moo…óon men ha…ói on immorde e gom…óim…ďe …ďen ?\" Alla ko √Ďaawoowo hakkunde mon √Ďalnde Darngal, Alla Wa…óaŇčtaa heefer…ďe …ďen laawol e hoore gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  4,142,"Pellet, naafiqii…ďe …ďen hino janfaade Alla, Kanko kadi ko O Yo…ďoowo …ďe. Si …ďe immanike julde nden, …ďe immoto ko …ďe aamu…ďe, hi…ďe yiinoo e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe jantotaako Alla si wanaa see…óa"
  4,143,"Hi…ďe na…ďa artira hakkunde …óum, …ďe alaa e …ďee …óoo …ďe alaa e …ďee …óaa. Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a he…ďantaa mo laawol"
  4,144,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, wata on jogitor heefer…ďe …ďen weldii…ďe ko wanaa gom…óim…ďe …ďen. E on faala nde wa…óanton Alla e dow moo…óon hujja …ďanngu…óo"
  4,145,"Pellet, naafiqii…ďe …ďen no ka ndenka yiite, a he…ďantaa …ďe ballo"
  4,146,"Si wanaa …ďen tuubu…ďe, …ďe mo∆ī∆īini, …ďe jogitii [diina] Alla …ďe la…ď…ďini diina ma…ď…ďe kan : …ďen …óon wonndii e gom…óim…ďe …ďen. Arma Alla Ye…óa gom…óim…ďe …ďen njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,147,"Ko hon…óum Alla Wa…óata e leptugol on, si on yettii [Mo] on gom…óinii [Mo] ? Alla Laatike Jaarnoowo Anndu…óo"
  4,148,"Alla Yi…óaa ko fee√Īi kon e bone immorde e kongol, si wanaa on too√Īaa…óo. Alla Laatike Nanoowo Anndu…óo"
  4,149,"Si on fe√Ī√Īinii mo∆ī∆īere, maa on suu…óii nde maa on yaafike gaay e bone, pellet, Alla Laatike Yaafotoo…óo Hattan…óo"
  4,150,"Pellet, …ďen won…ďe yeddude Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, hi…ďe faandii nde …ďe senndindirta hakkunde Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, hi…ďe wi'a :\"Me…óen gom…óina yoga men yedda yoga\", hi…ďe faala jogitaade hakkunde …óum …óon laawol"
  4,151,∆Āen …óon ko kam…ďe woni yeddu…ďe …ďen tigiri. Men Hebilanii heefer…ďe …ďen lepte hoynooje
  4,152,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, …ďe sen- ndindiraali hakkunde gooto e ma…ď…ďe, …ďen …óon, arma O Ye…óa …ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin. Alla Laatike Yaafotoo…óo Hinnotoo…óo"
  4,153,"Yim…ďe Defte …ďen no lamndo maa nde jippintaa e dow ma…ď…ďe Deftere immorde e ka kammu ! Gom…óii …ďe lamndinoke Muusaa ko …ďuri …óum mawnude : …ďe wi'i : \"Hollu Men Alla kene pettan \". Haacaango ngon nanngiri …ďe sabu too√Īe ma…ď…ďe …óen. Refti …ďe jogitii ngaari ndin …ďaawo nde ko ari …ďe e …ďanngan- nduyeeji. Men Yaafii gaay e …óum Men Okki Muusaa hujja …ďanngu…óo"
  4,154,"Men ∆Āamtiri dow ma…ď…ďe Tuur fello ngon sabu ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin, Men Wi'ani …ďe :\"Naatiree ka damal ko on naayii…ďe\", Men wi'ani …ďe : \"Wata on jaggitu e asewe on\", Men Nanngi e ma…ď…ďe ahadi tekkundi"
  4,155,"Ko sabu firtugol …ďe ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin, e yeddugol …ďe Aayeeje Alla …óen, e warugol …ďe Annabaa…ďe …ďen ko aldaa e goonga e wi'gol …ďe :\"∆Āer…óe amen …óen no sokii\". Si ko woni, Alla Notii e majje sabu keefe-raaku ma…ď…ďe ngun -…ďe gom…óintaa si wanaa see…óa"
  4,156,"e sabu keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe ngun, e konngol ma…ď…ďe ngol dow Maryama fenaande mawnde"
  4,157,"e wi'ugol …ďe : \"Menen men warii Iisaa Meme-sella, …ďi…ó…óo Maryama, Nulaa…óo Alla on\". ∆Āe waraali mo, …ďe fetaali mo, ko woni, o nanndinana …ďe. Pellet …ďen …ďen luutondir…ďe fii makko :…ďe wonii e sikkitaare fii makko. Alanaa …ďe e fii …óum anndal, si wanaa jokku- gol sikke, …ďe waraano mo e ta∆īoral(yananeede)"
  4,158,"Ko woni, Alla ∆Āamtu mo faade ka Makko. Alla Laatike Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,159,"Alaa hay gooto e yim…ďe Defte …ďen, si wanaa o gom…óinay mo ado maayde makko nden. √Ďalnde Dargal o laatoto seeditotoo…óo e hoore ma…ď…ďe"
  4,160,"Ko sabu too√Īe immorde e …ďen Alyahuudaa…ďe, Men Harmiannoo…ďe laa…ďu…ói …ói …ďe daginanoo e sabu sakkagol(faddagol) laawol Alla ngol ko …óuu…ói"
  4,161,"e ja…ďugol …ďe ngol ribaa, gom…óii …ďe ha…óaama e …óum, e √Īaamugol jawle yim…ďe …ďen e hoore meere. Men Hebilanii heefer…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe lepte muusu…óe"
  4,162,"Kono tutii…ďe …ďen e ganndal e ma…ď…ďe e gom…óim…ďe …ďen, hi…ďe gom…óini ko Jippinaa ko e maa…óa e kon ko Jippinaa ado maa…óa. E √Īii…ďnoo…ďe julde …ďen, e tottoo…ďe asakal …ďen, e gom…óim…ďe Alla e √Ďalaande Sakkitiinde nden, …ďen …óon, arma Men Okka …ďe njo…ďdi mawndi"
  4,163,"Menen Men Wahyinii e maa…óa wano Men Wahyiniri e Nuuhu e Annabaa…ďe …ďen …ďaawo makko. Men Wahyini faade e Ibraahiima, e Ismaa'iila, e Ishaaqa, e Yaaquuba, Taaniraa…ďe …ďen, e Iisaa, e Ayyuuba, e Yuunusa, e Haaruuna, e Sulaymaana. Men Okki Daawuuda Jabuura"
  4,164,E Nulaa…ďe …ďe Men Fillani maa fii mun ko adii e Nulaa…ďe …ďe Men fillanaaki ma fii mun. Alla Yewtidii e Muusaa Yewtude
  4,165,"Nulaa…ďe wewlinoo…ďe e jertinoo…ďe fii wata hujja wonan yim…ďe …ďen e hoore Alla …ďaawo Nulaa…ďe …ďen. Alla Laatike Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,166,"Kono Alla no Seedii kon ko O Jippini e maa…óa, O Jippinirii …óum Anndal Makko, Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďen no seeditoo. Alla Yonii Seedee"
  4,167,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe, …ďe faddii gaay e laawol Alla ngol, gom…óii …ďe majjii majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  4,168,"Pellet, …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe too√Īi, Alla Laatataaka yaafatoo…óo …ďe, wanaa nde O Fewnata …ďe laawol"
  4,169,"Si wanaa laawol Jahannama ngol, ko luttoo…ďe nder magge poomaa. ∆äum laatike newii…óum e dow Alla"
  4,170,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe ! Gom…óii Nulaa…óo on ardirii e mon goonga immorde e Joomi mon, gom…óinee ko mo∆ī∆īere mon. Si on yeddii, pellet, ko Alla Woodani kala ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike Anndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  4,171,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe Defte, wata on …ďurtin ka diina mon, wata on wowlu e hoore Alla si wanaa goonga. Pellet, Mema-sella Iisaa …ďi…ó…óo Maryama on, ko Nulaa…óo Alla e Daalol Makko ngol O Werlii e Maryama e ruuhu immorde ka Makko. Gom…óinee Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on, wata on wi'u [Alla ko] :\"Tato\". Ha…óitee, ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on. Anndee Alla ko Rewetee…óo Gooto. Senayee woodanii Mo nde …ďi…ó…óo laatantoo Mo ! Ko Kanko Woodani ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Yonii Hoolortee…óo"
  4,172,"Mema-sella on mawnitaaki nde o laatotoo jeyaa…óa Alla, wanaa Malaa'ikaa…ďe …ďa…ótinaa…ďe …ďen. Kala …ďurnitii…óo gaay e rewugol Mo o mawnintinii, ma O Moo…ďitoy…ďe faade ka Makko …ďe denndaangal"
  4,173,"Si tawii ko …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói, O Timminanay …ďe njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe ndin, O ∆Āeydana e ∆Āural Makko ngol. ∆Āeya …ďurnitii…ďe mawnintinii, O Leptay…ďe lepte muusu…óe, …ďe he…ďanoytaa…ďe gaanin Alla, gi…óo wanaa ballo"
  4,174,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe ! Gom…óii hujja arii e moo…óon immorde ka Joomi mon, Men Jippinii faade e moo…óon annnora …ďanngu…óo"
  4,175,"Si tawii ko …ďen gom…óim…ďe Alla …ďe jogiitii nde, arma O Naada …ďe e Yurmeende immorde ka Makko e ∆Āural, O Fewna …ďe faade e Makko laawol focciingol"
  4,176,"Hi…ďe faltino maa. Maaku : \"Alla no Falta on fii rona-jala : si ne…ó…óo maayii o alaa …ďi…ó…óo himo mari banndiraawo [debbo], no woodani on feccere e kon ko o acci. Kanko kadi o ronay mo si tawii o alaa …ďi…ó…óo. Si …ďe laatike …ói…óo, hino woodani …ďe tata…ďe …ói…ói e kon ko o acci. Si …ďe laatike si…ó…óu…ďe wor…ďe e rew…ďe, hino woodani gorko on ge…ďal rew…ďe …ói…óo. Alla no ∆Āannginannde on fii wata on majju. Alla ko Anndu…óo kala huunde"